{"data":[{"date":"13:47 22/07","title":"TR\u1ef0C TI\u1ebeP Kh\u00e1nh H\u00f2a 0-0 H\u1ea3i Ph\u00f2ng (H1)","type":"B\u00f3ng \u0111\u00e1 Vi\u1ec7t Nam","img_url":"https://static.bongda24h.vn/medias/thumnail/2018/7/22/khanh-hoa-vs-hai-phong-vong-20-vleague-2018.jpg","new_desc":"<link href='https://bongda24h.vn/websites/css/stylemobilev3.css?v=3' rel='stylesheet' type='text/css' /><style>body{margin:0px; padding:3px; font-size: 20px;}*{font-size:20px !important;}.articlerelatepannel { display:none; padding: 6px;  margin-top:5px; margin-bottom:5px; background-color:#f7f7f7; border:solid 1px #0cac0c}.mediaplayercontent{display:none;}h1{font-size:24px; font-weight:bold; color:black;}h2{font-weight:bold; color:black; width:100%; margin-top:5px !important;}h3{font-weight:bold; color:black;}iframe{display:none;}</style><div class='chitiet_tin'><h2>Tr\u1ef1c ti\u1ebfp Kh\u00e1nh H\u00f2a vs H\u1ea3i Ph\u00f2ng: C\u1eadp nh\u1eadt li\u00ean t\u1ee5c di\u1ec5n bi\u1ebfn t\u01b0\u1eddng thu\u1eadt t\u00ecnh hu\u1ed1ng k\u1ebft qu\u1ea3 b\u00f3ng \u0111\u00e1 tr\u1eadn \u0111\u1ea5u Kh\u00e1nh H\u00f2a vs H\u1ea3i Ph\u00f2ng v\u00f2ng 20 gi\u1ea3i v\u00f4 \u0111\u1ecbch qu\u1ed1c gia V\u0110QG Vi\u1ec7t Nam V-League 2018 l\u00fac 17h00 chi\u1ec1u ng\u00e0y h\u00f4m nay 22/7.</h2><h2>Tr\u1ef1c ti\u1ebfp Kh\u00e1nh H\u00f2a vs H\u1ea3i Ph\u00f2ng: C\u1eadp nh\u1eadt li\u00ean t\u1ee5c di\u1ec5n bi\u1ebfn t\u01b0\u1eddng thu\u1eadt t\u00ecnh hu\u1ed1ng k\u1ebft qu\u1ea3 b\u00f3ng \u0111\u00e1 tr\u1eadn \u0111\u1ea5u Kh\u00e1nh H\u00f2a vs H\u1ea3i Ph\u00f2ng v\u00f2ng 20 gi\u1ea3i v\u00f4 \u0111\u1ecbch qu\u1ed1c gia V\u0110QG Vi\u1ec7t Nam V-League 2018 l\u00fac 17h00 chi\u1ec1u ng\u00e0y h\u00f4m nay 22/7.</h2>\r\nKh\u00f4ng xem \u0111\u01b0\u01a1c, vui l\u00f2ng click v\u00e0o \u0111\u00e2y <span href=\"https://bongda24h.vn/truc-tiep-bong-da/tran-dau/khanh-hoa-vs-hai-phong-vong-20-vleague-2018-372-191779.html\" target=\"_blank\"><span style=\"color: rgb(128, 0, 0);\"><u><strong>TR\u1ef0C TI\u1ebeP KH\u00c1NH H\u00d2A VS H\u1ea2I PH\u00d2NG</strong></u></span></span><br>\r\n<br></div><advbottom>","new_url":"","id":"4490","checkdouble":"191779"},{"date":"14:12 22/07","title":"\u0110\u00e3 r\u00f5 ch\u1ea5n th\u01b0\u01a1ng c\u1ee7a tuy\u1ec3n th\u1ee7 Ph\u1ea1m Xu\u00e2n M\u1ea1nh","type":"B\u00f3ng \u0111\u00e1 Vi\u1ec7t Nam","img_url":"https://static.bongda24h.vn/medias/thumnail/2018/7/21/da-ro-chan-thuong-cua-tuyen-thu-pham-xuan-manh.png","new_desc":"<link href='https://bongda24h.vn/websites/css/stylemobilev3.css?v=3' rel='stylesheet' type='text/css' /><style>body{margin:0px; padding:3px; font-size: 20px;}*{font-size:20px !important;}.articlerelatepannel { display:none; padding: 6px;  margin-top:5px; margin-bottom:5px; background-color:#f7f7f7; border:solid 1px #0cac0c}.mediaplayercontent{display:none;}h1{font-size:24px; font-weight:bold; color:black;}h2{font-weight:bold; color:black; width:100%; margin-top:5px !important;}h3{font-weight:bold; color:black;}iframe{display:none;}</style><div class='chitiet_tin'><h2>CLB SLNA m\u1edbi \u0111\u00e2y \u0111\u00e3 th\u00f4ng b\u00e1o v\u1ec1 t\u00ecnh tr\u1ea1ng ch\u1ea5n th\u01b0\u01a1ng c\u1ee7a h\u1eadu v\u1ec7 c\u00e1nh Ph\u1ea1m Xu\u00e2n M\u1ea1nh sau tr\u1eadn \u0111\u1ea5u v\u1edbi HAGL chi\u1ec1u t\u1ed1i qua 21/7.</h2><h2>Ch\u1ea5n th\u01b0\u01a1ng c\u1ee7a h\u1eadu v\u1ec7 Ph\u1ea1m Xu\u00e2n M\u1ea1nh kh\u00f4ng nghi\u00eam tr\u1ecdng</h2>\r\n<div style=\"text-align: center; width: 100%\" class=\"imagecontainer\">\r\n<table style=\"text-align: center; width:100%;\">\r\n    <tbody>\r\n        <tr style=\"width:100%;\">\r\n            <td style=\"width: 100%;\" align=\"center\"><em><img style=\"border: none\" alt=\"SLNA\" title=\"SLNA\" src=\"https://static.bongda24h.vn/medias/mobile/2018/7/21/da-ro-chan-thuong-cua-tuyen-thu-pham-xuan-manh.png\" /></em></td>\r\n        </tr>\r\n        <tr>\r\n            <td><em>Ph\u1ea1m Xu\u00e2n M\u1ea1nh (tr\u00e1i) ghi d\u1ea5u \u1ea5n trong chi\u1ebfn th\u1eafng c\u1ee7a SLNA tr\u01b0\u1edbc HAGL</em></td>\r\n        </tr>\r\n    </tbody>\r\n</table>\r\n</div>\r\n<p style=\"text-align: justify;\">Trong tr\u1eadn \u0111\u1ea5u gi\u1eefa SLNA vs HAGL t\u1ea1i v\u00f2ng 20 V-League di\u1ec5n ra chi\u1ec1u 21/7, h\u1eadu v\u1ec7 c\u00e1nh Ph\u1ea1m Xu\u00e2n M\u1ea1nh c\u1ee7a \u0111\u1ed9i ch\u1ee7 nh\u00e0 \u0111\u00e3 kh\u00f4ng may g\u1eb7p ph\u1ea3i m\u1ed9t ch\u1ea5n th\u01b0\u01a1ng. <o:p></o:p></p>\r\n<p style=\"text-align: justify;\">Sau m\u1ed9t n\u1ed7 l\u1ef1c truy c\u1ea3n&nbsp;pha l\u00ean b\u00f3ng c\u1ee7a c\u00e1c c\u1ea7u th\u1ee7 HAGL, Xu\u00e2n M\u1ea1nh&nbsp;\u0111\u00e3 b\u1ecb \u0111au v\u00e0 ph\u1ea3i nh\u1edd t\u1edbi s\u1ef1 tr\u1ee3 gi\u00fap c\u1ee7a c\u00e1c nh\u00e2n vi\u00ean y t\u1ebf. \u0110i\u1ec1u n\u00e0y kh\u00f4ng ch\u1ec9 khi\u1ebfn C\u0110V SLNA lo l\u1eafng m\u00e0 ch\u1eafc h\u1eb3n HLV Park Hang Seo c\u0169ng \u0111\u1ee9ng ng\u1ed3i kh\u00f4ng y\u00ean khi nghe th\u00f4ng tin v\u1ec1 c\u1eadu h\u1ecdc tr\u00f2 c\u1ee7a m\u00ecnh. Ch\u1ec9 c\u00f2n \u00edt ng\u00e0y n\u1eefa \u0110T Olympic Vi\u1ec7t Nam s\u1ebd t\u1eadp trung v\u00e0 n\u1ebfu Xu\u00e2n M\u1ea1nh kh\u00f4ng thi \u0111\u1ea5u, \u0111\u00e2y th\u1ef1c s\u1ef1 l\u00e0 m\u1ed9t s\u1ef1 v\u1eafng m\u1eb7t r\u1ea5t \u0111\u00e1ng ti\u1ebfc.<o:p></o:p></p>\r\n</div><mobileadv><link href='https://bongda24h.vn/websites/css/stylemobilev3.css?v=3' rel='stylesheet' type='text/css' /><style>body{margin:0px; padding:3px; font-size: 20px;}*{font-size:20px !important;}.articlerelatepannel { display:none; padding: 6px;  margin-top:5px; margin-bottom:5px; background-color:#f7f7f7; border:solid 1px #0cac0c}.mediaplayercontent{display:none;}h1{font-size:24px; font-weight:bold; color:black;}h2{font-weight:bold; color:black; width:100%; margin-top:5px !important;}h3{font-weight:bold; color:black;}iframe{display:none;}</style><div class='chitiet_tin'><p style=\"text-align: justify;\">Tuy nhi\u00ean theo th\u00f4ng tin m\u1edbi nh\u1ea5t t\u1eeb \u0111\u1ed9i b\u00f3ng x\u1ee9 Ngh\u1ec7, ch\u1ea5n th\u01b0\u01a1ng c\u1ee7a h\u1eadu v\u1ec7 Ph\u1ea1m Xu\u00e2n M\u1ea1nh th\u1ef1c s\u1ef1 kh\u00f4ng nghi\u00eam tr\u1ecdng. Tuy\u1ec3n th\u1ee7 U23 Vi\u1ec7t Nam ch\u1ec9 b\u1ecb tr\u1eb9o ch\u00e2n v\u00e0 th\u1eddi gian h\u1ed3i ph\u1ee5c nhanh h\u01a1n nhi\u1ec1u so v\u1edbi tr\u01b0\u1eddng h\u1ee3p b\u1ecb l\u1eadt c\u1ed5 ch\u00e2n.<o:p></o:p></p>\r\n<p style=\"text-align: justify;\">V\u00ec th\u1ebf Xu\u00e2n M\u1ea1nh ch\u1ec9 c\u1ea7n v\u00e0i ng\u00e0y ngh\u1ec9 ng\u01a1i s\u1ebd c\u00f3 th\u1ec3 tr\u1edf l\u1ea1i thi \u0111\u1ea5u. Theo k\u1ebf ho\u1ea1ch anh c\u00f9ng ng\u01b0\u1eddi \u0111\u1ed3ng \u0111\u1ed9i Ph\u1ea1m V\u0103n \u0110\u1ee9c ra H\u00e0 N\u1ed9i \u0111\u1ec3 h\u1ed9i qu\u00e2n \u0110T Olympic Vi\u1ec7t Nam v\u00e0o ng\u00e0y mai 23/7.</p>\r\n<div class=\"articlerelatepannel\">\r\n<div class=\"articlerelate2\"><span href=\"/bong-da-viet-nam/nhung-diem-nhan-dang-chu-y-sau-tran-thang-cua-slna-truoc-hagl-168-191757.html\"><img src=\"https://static.bongda24h.vn/medias/thumnail/2018/7/21/nhung-diem-nhan-dang-chu-y-sau-tran-thang-cua-slna-truoc-hagl.jpg\" alt=\"\" /></span><span href=\"/bong-da-viet-nam/nhung-diem-nhan-dang-chu-y-sau-tran-thang-cua-slna-truoc-hagl-168-191757.html\">Nh\u1eefng \u0111i\u1ec3m nh\u1ea5n \u0111\u00e1ng ch\u00fa \u00fd sau tr\u1eadn th\u1eafng 3-1 c\u1ee7a SLNA tr\u01b0\u1edbc HAGL</span><br />\r\n\u0110\u01b0\u1ee3c thi \u0111\u1ea5u tr\u00ean s\u00e2n nh\u00e0, CLB SLNA \u0111\u00e3 c\u00f3 chi\u1ebfn th\u1eafng 3-1 tr\u01b0\u1edbc c\u00e1c c\u1ea7u th\u1ee7 HAGL. V\u00e0 d\u01b0\u1edbi \u0111\u00e2y l\u00e0 nh\u1eefng \u0111i\u1ec3m nh\u1ea5n \u1edf tr\u1eadn \u0111\u1ea5u n\u00e0y.</div>\r\n<div class=\"articlerelate2\"><span href=\"/bong-da-viet-nam/ha-dep-hagl-slna-bat-kip-ky-luc-vleague-13-nam-truoc-168-191752.html\"><img src=\"https://static.bongda24h.vn/medias/thumnail/2018/7/21/ha-dep-hagl-slna-bat-kip-ky-luc-vleague-13-nam-truoc.jpg\" alt=\"\" /></span><span href=\"/bong-da-viet-nam/ha-dep-hagl-slna-bat-kip-ky-luc-vleague-13-nam-truoc-168-191752.html\">H\u1ea1 \u0111\u1eb9p HAGL, SLNA b\u1eaft k\u1ecbp k\u1ef7 l\u1ee5c V-League 13 n\u0103m tr\u01b0\u1edbc</span><br />\r\n\u0110\u1ed9i b\u00f3ng x\u1ee9 Ngh\u1ec7 v\u1eeba b\u1eaft k\u1ecbp k\u1ef7 l\u1ee5c \u0111\u00e3 t\u1ed3n t\u1ea1i 13 n\u0103m t\u1ea1i V-League do CLB G\u1ea1ch \u0110\u1ed3ng T\u00e2m Long An thi\u1ebft l\u1eadp sau chi\u1ebfn th\u1eafng tr\u01b0\u1edbc HAGL.</div>\r\n</div>\r\n<p style=\"text-align: justify;\">Minh Long (TTVN)<span style=\"font-size:16.0pt;line-height:115%\"><o:p></o:p></span></p></div><advbottom>","new_url":"","id":"4489","checkdouble":"191780"},{"date":"14:37 22/07","title":"HLV H\u00e0 N\u1ed9i tuy\u00ean b\u1ed1 t\u1ef1 tin sau tr\u1eadn th\u1eafng Thanh H\u00f3a","type":"B\u00f3ng \u0111\u00e1 Vi\u1ec7t Nam","img_url":"https://static.bongda24h.vn/medias/thumnail/2018/6/3/hlv-ha-noi-tuyen-bo-tu-tin-sau-tran-thang-thanh-hoa.JPG","new_desc":"<link href='https://bongda24h.vn/websites/css/stylemobilev3.css?v=3' rel='stylesheet' type='text/css' /><style>body{margin:0px; padding:3px; font-size: 20px;}*{font-size:20px !important;}.articlerelatepannel { display:none; padding: 6px;  margin-top:5px; margin-bottom:5px; background-color:#f7f7f7; border:solid 1px #0cac0c}.mediaplayercontent{display:none;}h1{font-size:24px; font-weight:bold; color:black;}h2{font-weight:bold; color:black; width:100%; margin-top:5px !important;}h3{font-weight:bold; color:black;}iframe{display:none;}</style><div class='chitiet_tin'><h2>Chia s\u1ebb v\u1edbi b\u00e1o gi\u1edbi, nh\u00e0 c\u1ea7m qu\u00e2n c\u1ee7a CLB H\u00e0 N\u1ed9i, HLV Chu \u0110\u00ecnh Nghi\u00eam kh\u1eb3ng \u0111\u1ecbnh \u0111\u1ed9i nh\u00e0 s\u1ebd v\u00f4 \u0111\u1ecbch s\u1edbm v\u00e0i v\u00f2ng \u0111\u1ea5u n\u1ebfu ti\u1ebfp t\u1ee5c thi \u0111\u1ea5u nh\u01b0 hi\u1ec7n t\u1ea1i.</h2><p style=\"text-align: justify;\">T\u1ea1i v\u00f2ng 20 V-League, CLB H\u00e0 N\u1ed9i \u0111\u00e3 c\u00f3 chi\u1ebfn th\u1eafng ng\u01b0\u1ee3c 3-2 tr\u01b0\u1edbc FLC Thanh H\u00f3a.\u00a0<o:p></o:p>\u0110\u00e1ng ch\u00fa \u00fd \u1edf l\u01b0\u1ee3t \u0111i, H\u00e0 N\u1ed9i c\u0169ng l\u00e0 \u0111\u1ed9i gi\u00e0nh ph\u1ea7n th\u1eafng d\u00f9 \u0111\u1ec3 cho Thanh H\u00f3a ghi b\u00e0n d\u1eabn tr\u01b0\u1edbc.<br>\r\n<o:p></o:p></p>\r\n<div style=\"text-align: center; width: 100%\" class=\"imagecontainer\">\r\n<table style=\"text-align: center; width:100%;\">\r\n    <tbody>\r\n        <tr style=\"width:100%;\">\r\n            <td style=\"width: 100%;\" align=\"center\"><img style=\"border: none\" alt=\"HLV Chu \u0110\u00ecnh Nghi\u00eam tuy\u00ean b\u1ed1 t\u1ef1 tin sau tr\u1eadn th\u1eafng Thanh H\u00f3a h\u00ecnh \u1ea3nh\" title=\"HLV Chu \u0110\u00ecnh Nghi\u00eam tuy\u00ean b\u1ed1 t\u1ef1 tin sau tr\u1eadn th\u1eafng Thanh H\u00f3a h\u00ecnh \u1ea3nh\" src=\"https://static.bongda24h.vn/medias/mobile/2018/6/3/Thang-dam-CLB-TPHCM,-HLV-Chu-Dinh-Nghiem-noi-ve-co-hoi-vo-dich-hinh-anh.JPG\"></td>\r\n        </tr>\r\n        <tr>\r\n            <td><em>HLV Chu \u0110\u00ecnh Nghi\u00eam ph\u00e1t bi\u1ec3u \u0111\u1ea7y t\u1ef1 tin sau chi\u1ebfn th\u1eafng tr\u01b0\u1edbc Thanh H\u00f3a</em></td>\r\n        </tr>\r\n    </tbody>\r\n</table>\r\n</div>\r\n<p style=\"text-align: justify;\">V\u01b0\u1ee3t qua m\u1ed9t \u0111\u1ed9i b\u00f3ng m\u1ea1nh nh\u01b0 Thanh H\u00f3a \u1edf c\u1ea3 hai l\u01b0\u1ee3t tr\u1eadn, \u0111i\u1ec1u n\u00e0y \u0111\u00e3 ch\u1ee9ng minh s\u1ee9c m\u1ea1nh c\u1ee7a \u0111\u1ed9i b\u00f3ng H\u00e0 N\u1ed9i. \u1ede th\u1eddi \u0111i\u1ec3m hi\u1ec7n t\u1ea1i, h\u1ecd \u0111\u00e3 b\u1ecf xa nh\u00f3m b\u00e1m \u0111u\u1ed5i t\u1edbi 17 \u0111i\u1ec3m. V\u00e0 \u0111i\u1ec1u n\u00e0y c\u0169ng gi\u00fap HLV Chu \u0110\u00ecnh Nghi\u00eam t\u1ef1 tin kh\u1eb3ng \u0111\u1ecbnh \u0111\u1ed9i nh\u00e0 s\u1ebd s\u1edbm v\u00f4 \u0111\u1ecbch tr\u01b0\u1edbc v\u00e0i v\u00f2ng \u0111\u1ea5u n\u1eefa.<o:p></o:p></p>\r\n</div><mobileadv><link href='https://bongda24h.vn/websites/css/stylemobilev3.css?v=3' rel='stylesheet' type='text/css' /><style>body{margin:0px; padding:3px; font-size: 20px;}*{font-size:20px !important;}.articlerelatepannel { display:none; padding: 6px;  margin-top:5px; margin-bottom:5px; background-color:#f7f7f7; border:solid 1px #0cac0c}.mediaplayercontent{display:none;}h1{font-size:24px; font-weight:bold; color:black;}h2{font-weight:bold; color:black; width:100%; margin-top:5px !important;}h3{font-weight:bold; color:black;}iframe{display:none;}</style><div class='chitiet_tin'><p style=\"text-align: justify;\">Chia s\u1ebb sau bu\u1ed5i h\u1ecdp b\u00e1o t\u1ea1i v\u00f2ng 20 V-League, v\u1ecb thuy\u1ec1n tr\u01b0\u1edfng \u0111\u1ed9i b\u00f3ng th\u1ee7 \u0111\u00f4 cho hay: \u201c\u0110\u1ebfn th\u1eddi \u0111i\u1ec3m n\u00e0y, n\u1ebfu so v\u1edbi s\u1ed1 \u0111i\u1ec3m m\u00e0 ch\u00fang t\u00f4i \u0111ang c\u00f3, H\u00e0 N\u1ed9i FC \u0111\u00e3 v\u00f4 \u0111\u1ecbch. B\u1edfi so v\u1edbi m\u1ecdi n\u0103m, c\u00e1c \u0111\u1ed9i ch\u1ec9 c\u1ea7n 48 ho\u1eb7c 50 \u0111i\u1ec3m l\u00e0 \u0111\u00e3 c\u00f3 th\u1ec3 v\u00f4 \u0111\u1ecbch, ngo\u1ea1i tr\u1eeb B\u00ecnh D\u01b0\u01a1ng l\u00ean ng\u00f4i khi h\u1ecd c\u00f3 53 \u0111i\u1ec3m. <o:p></o:p></p>\r\n<p style=\"text-align: justify;\">Hi\u1ec7n t\u1ea1i, H\u00e0 N\u1ed9i FC \u0111ang \u0111\u01b0\u1ee3c 51 \u0111i\u1ec3m v\u00e0 ch\u00fang t\u00f4i \u0111\u00e3 \u1edf r\u1ea5t g\u1ea7n ng\u00f4i v\u01b0\u01a1ng. Hi\u1ec7n t\u1ea1i, ch\u00fang t\u00f4i ch\u1ec9 ch\u1edd Sanna.KH s\u1ea3y ch\u00e2n, ho\u1eb7c c\u00e1c \u0111\u1ed1i th\u1ee7 g\u1eb7p nhau l\u00e0 H\u00e0 N\u1ed9i FC s\u1ebd l\u00ean ng\u00f4i v\u00f4 \u0111\u1ecbch <span href=\"https://bongda24h.vn/vleague-c291-p1.html\" target=\"_blank\">V.League 2018</span>\u201d.<o:p></o:p></p>\r\n<p style=\"text-align: justify;\">N\u00f3i v\u1ec1 tr\u1eadn th\u1eafng v\u1eeba r\u1ed3i t\u1ea1i Thanh H\u00f3a, nh\u00e0 c\u1ea7m qu\u00e2n ng\u01b0\u1eddi x\u1ee9 Thanh cho hay: \u00a0\u201cK\u1ebft qu\u1ea3 n\u00e0y th\u1ef1c s\u1ef1 t\u1ed1t cho \u0111\u1ed9i b\u00f3ng. H\u00f4m nay, m\u1eb7t s\u00e2n th\u1eddi ti\u1ebft kh\u00f4ng \u1ee7ng h\u1ed9, to\u00e0n \u0111\u1ed9i ph\u1ea3i t\u1eeb b\u1ecf l\u1ed1i ch\u01a1i quen thu\u1ed9c \u0111\u1ec3 \u0111\u00e1 b\u00f3ng d\u00e0i. Tr\u1eadn \u0111\u1ea5u n\u00e0y c\u0169ng gi\u1ed1ng nh\u01b0 m\u1ecdi n\u0103m, H\u00e0 N\u1ed9i FC b\u1ecb th\u1ee7ng l\u01b0\u1edbi tr\u01b0\u1edbc, nh\u01b0ng may m\u1eafn to\u00e0n \u0111\u1ed9i v\u1eabn gi\u1eef v\u1eefng \u0111\u01b0\u1ee3c tinh th\u1ea7n, t\u1eadp trung \u0111\u1ec3 b\u00ecnh t\u0129nh ch\u01a1i l\u1ea1i v\u00e0 c\u00f3 chi\u1ebfn th\u1eafng ng\u01b0\u1ee3c d\u00f2ng\u201d.<o:p></o:p></p>\r\n<p style=\"text-align: justify;\">\u1ede v\u00f2ng \u0111\u1ea5u ti\u1ebfp theo, H\u00e0 N\u1ed9i s\u1ebd g\u1eb7p \u0111\u1ed9i b\u00f3ng \u0111ang c\u00f3 phong \u0111\u1ed9 r\u1ea5t cao hi\u1ec7n nay l\u00e0 SLNA tr\u00ean s\u00e2n H\u00e0ng \u0110\u1eaby. Tuy nhi\u00ean tr\u1eadn \u0111\u1ea5u n\u00e0y s\u1ebd di\u1ec5n ra v\u00e0o \u0111\u1ea7u th\u00e1ng 9 t\u1edbi do gi\u1ea3i V-League \u0111\u00e3 t\u1ea1m ngh\u1ec9 \u0111\u1ec3 \u0110T Olympic Vi\u1ec7t Nam t\u1eadp trung chu\u1ea9n b\u1ecb cho ASIAD 2018.</p>\r\n<div class=\"mediaplayercontent\" data-href=\"https://video.bongda24h.vn/medias/MP4/2018/7/21/Highlight-Thanh-Hoa-vs-Ha-Noi.mp4\" data-width=\"480\" data-height=\"320\" data-type=\"m4v\"><img src=\"/Images/video-chi-tiet.jpg\" style=\"width: 300px; height:220px\" alt=\"\"></div>\r\n<p style=\"text-align: justify;\">Minh Long (TTVN)<span style=\"font-size:16.0pt;line-height:115%\"><o:p></o:p></span></p></div><advbottom>","new_url":"","id":"4488","checkdouble":"191784"},{"date":"14:51 22/07","title":"L\u0110B\u0110 ch\u00e2u \u00c1 AFC n\u00f3i g\u00ec v\u1ec1 kh\u1ea3 n\u0103ng b\u1ed1c th\u0103m l\u1ea1i ASIAD?","type":"B\u00f3ng \u0111\u00e1 Vi\u1ec7t Nam","img_url":"https://static.bongda24h.vn/medias/thumnail/2018/7/5/ldbd-chau-a-afc-noi-gi-ve-kha-nang-boc-tham-lai-asiad.png","new_desc":"<link href='https://bongda24h.vn/websites/css/stylemobilev3.css?v=3' rel='stylesheet' type='text/css' /><style>body{margin:0px; padding:3px; font-size: 20px;}*{font-size:20px !important;}.articlerelatepannel { display:none; padding: 6px;  margin-top:5px; margin-bottom:5px; background-color:#f7f7f7; border:solid 1px #0cac0c}.mediaplayercontent{display:none;}h1{font-size:24px; font-weight:bold; color:black;}h2{font-weight:bold; color:black; width:100%; margin-top:5px !important;}h3{font-weight:bold; color:black;}iframe{display:none;}</style><div class='chitiet_tin'><h2>Chia s\u1ebb v\u1edbi b\u00e1o gi\u1edbi, ng\u01b0\u1eddi \u0111\u1ee9ng \u0111\u1ea7u AFC, T\u1ed5ng th\u01b0 k\u00fd Windsor John Paul kh\u1eb3ng \u0111\u1ecbnh t\u1ed5 ch\u1ee9c n\u00e0y kh\u00f4ng can thi\u1ec7p v\u00e0o quy\u1ebft \u0111\u1ecbnh b\u1ed1c th\u0103m l\u1ea1i ASIAD 2018.\r\n\r\n</h2><h2>AFC\u00a0<span style=\"text-align: justify;\">kh\u00f4ng can thi\u1ec7p vi\u1ec7c b\u1ed1c th\u0103m l\u1ea1i ASIAD\u00a0</span></h2>\r\n<p style=\"text-align: justify;\">Nh\u01b0 nh\u1eefng th\u00f4ng tin \u0111\u00e3 chia s\u1ebb, sau khi hai qu\u1ed1c gia UAE v\u00e0 Palestine g\u1eedi ki\u1ebfn ngh\u1ecb v\u1ec1 vi\u1ec7c h\u1ecd kh\u00f4ng \u0111\u01b0\u1ee3c tham d\u1ef1 m\u00f4n b\u00f3ng \u0111\u00e1 nam t\u1ea1i ASIAD 2018, \u0111\u00e3 c\u00f3 nh\u1eefng th\u00f4ng tin v\u1ec1 vi\u1ec7c s\u1ebd b\u1ed1c th\u0103m l\u1ea1i gi\u1ea3i \u0111\u1ea5u n\u00e0y.<o:p></o:p></p>\r\n<p style=\"text-align: justify;\">Nhi\u1ec1u \u00fd ki\u1ebfn cho r\u1eb1ng L\u0110B\u0110 ch\u00e2u \u00c1 AFC \u0111\u00e3 h\u1ed1i th\u00fac n\u01b0\u1edbc ch\u1ee7 nh\u00e0 Indonesia t\u1ed5 ch\u1ee9c b\u1ed1c th\u0103m l\u1ea1i c\u00e1c b\u1ea3ng m\u1ed9t l\u1ea7n n\u1eefa nh\u01b0ng n\u01b0\u1edbc ch\u1ee7 nh\u00e0 v\u1eabn \u0111ang ph\u00e2n v\u00e2n v\u1ec1 h\u00ecnh th\u1ee9c gi\u1ea3i quy\u1ebft.<o:p></o:p></p>\r\n</div><mobileadv><link href='https://bongda24h.vn/websites/css/stylemobilev3.css?v=3' rel='stylesheet' type='text/css' /><style>body{margin:0px; padding:3px; font-size: 20px;}*{font-size:20px !important;}.articlerelatepannel { display:none; padding: 6px;  margin-top:5px; margin-bottom:5px; background-color:#f7f7f7; border:solid 1px #0cac0c}.mediaplayercontent{display:none;}h1{font-size:24px; font-weight:bold; color:black;}h2{font-weight:bold; color:black; width:100%; margin-top:5px !important;}h3{font-weight:bold; color:black;}iframe{display:none;}</style><div class='chitiet_tin'><p style=\"text-align: justify;\">Tuy nhi\u00ean n\u00f3i v\u1ec1 chuy\u1ec7n n\u00e0y, \u00f4ng Windsor John Paul\u00a0- T\u1ed5ng th\u01b0 k\u00fd\u00a0AFC kh\u1eb3ng \u0111\u1ecbnh kh\u00f4ng hay bi\u1ebft g\u00ec v\u1ec1 r\u1eafc r\u1ed1i \u0111ang di\u1ec5n ra \u1edf m\u00f4n b\u00f3ng \u0111\u00e1 nam t\u1ea1i ASIAD 2018.\u00a0<o:p></o:p>\u201cCh\u00fang t\u00f4i ch\u1ec9 h\u1ed7 tr\u1ee3 ch\u1ee9 kh\u00f4ng can thi\u1ec7p vi\u1ec7c b\u1ed1c th\u0103m l\u1ea1i\u201d - \u00d4ng Datuk Windsor John Paul\u00a0 chia s\u1ebb. <o:p></o:p></p>\r\n<p style=\"text-align: justify;\">V\u1ecb n\u00e0y n\u00f3i th\u00eam: \"Th\u1eddi \u0111i\u1ec3m n\u00e0y, \u1ee6y ban Olympic ch\u00e2u \u00c1 (OCA) v\u00e0 INASGOC (\u1ee6y ban Olympic Indonesia) ch\u01b0a th\u00f4ng b\u00e1o g\u00ec v\u1ec1 bu\u1ed5i b\u1ed1c th\u0103m. Ch\u00fang t\u00f4i ch\u01b0a nh\u1eadn \u0111\u01b0\u1ee3c v\u0103n b\u1ea3n n\u00e0o t\u1eeb ph\u00eda nh\u00e0 t\u1ed5 ch\u1ee9c \u0111\u1ecba ph\u01b0\u01a1ng. C\u00f3 th\u1ec3 m\u1ecdi chuy\u1ec7n s\u1ebd \u0111\u01b0\u1ee3c gi\u1ea3i quy\u1ebft v\u00e0o tu\u1ea7n t\u1edbi\u201d.<o:p></o:p></p>\r\n<p style=\"text-align: justify;\">\u201cCh\u00fang t\u00f4i ch\u1ec9 bi\u1ebft l\u00e0 bu\u1ed5i b\u1ed1c th\u0103m ng\u00e0y 5/7 \u0111\u00e3 xong nh\u01b0ng v\u00ec 2 \u0111\u1ed9i ch\u01b0a c\u00f3 t\u00ean trong b\u1ea3ng \u0111\u1ea5u n\u00ean ph\u1ea3i ti\u1ebfp t\u1ee5c ch\u1edd. Quy\u1ebft \u0111\u1ecbnh c\u00f3 b\u1ed1c th\u0103m l\u1ea1i hay kh\u00f4ng v\u00e0 gi\u1ea3i quy\u1ebft nh\u01b0 th\u1ebf n\u00e0o l\u00e0 quy\u1ec1n c\u1ee7a OCA v\u00e0 INASGOC\u201d.<o:p></o:p></p>\r\n<p style=\"text-align: justify;\">Tr\u01b0\u1edbc \u0111\u00f3 nhi\u1ec1u ngu\u1ed3n tin t\u1ea1i Indonesia cho r\u1eb1ng l\u1ec5 b\u1ed1c th\u0103m l\u1ea1i m\u00f4n b\u00f3ng \u0111\u00e1 Nam ASIAD s\u1ebd di\u1ec5n ra v\u00e0o th\u1ee9 Hai t\u1edbi, tuy nhi\u00ean n\u01b0\u1edbc ch\u1ee7 nh\u00e0 c\u0169ng kh\u1eb3ng \u0111\u1ecbnh r\u1eb1ng vi\u1ec7c b\u1ed1c th\u0103m l\u1ea1i t\u1ea5t c\u1ea3 c\u00e1c \u0111\u1ed9i l\u00e0 \u0111i\u1ec1u b\u1ea5t kh\u1ea3 thi v\u00e0 h\u1ecd mu\u1ed1n b\u1ed1c th\u0103m \u0111\u01b0a 2 \u0111\u1ed9i UAE v\u00e0 Palestine v\u00e0o 2 b\u1ea3ng \u0111\u1ea5u b\u1ea5t k\u1ef3. T\u1ee9c l\u00e0 c\u00f3 2 b\u1ea3ng \u0111\u1ea5u s\u1ebd c\u00f3 5 \u0111\u1ed9i, 2 \u0111\u1ed9i nh\u1ea5t v\u00e0 nh\u00ec c\u00f9ng 4 \u0111\u1ed9i h\u1ea1ng 3 c\u00f3 th\u00e0nh t\u00edch t\u1ed1t s\u1ebd v\u00e0o v\u00f2ng knock-out.</p>\r\n<div style=\"text-align: center; width: 100%\" class=\"imagecontainer\">\r\n<table style=\"text-align: center; width:100%;\">\r\n    <tbody>\r\n        <tr style=\"width:100%;\">\r\n            <td style=\"width: 100%;\" align=\"center\"><img style=\"border: none\" alt=\"L\u0110B\u0110 ch\u00e2u \u00c1 AFC n\u00f3i g\u00ec v\u1ec1 kh\u1ea3 n\u0103ng b\u1ed1c th\u0103m l\u1ea1i ASIAD h\u00ecnh \u1ea3nh\" title=\"L\u0110B\u0110 ch\u00e2u \u00c1 AFC n\u00f3i g\u00ec v\u1ec1 kh\u1ea3 n\u0103ng b\u1ed1c th\u0103m l\u1ea1i ASIAD h\u00ecnh \u1ea3nh\" src=\"https://static.bongda24h.vn/medias/mobile/2018/7/5/ldbd-chau-a-muon-boc-tham-lai-mon-bong-da-nam-asiad.png\"></td>\r\n        </tr>\r\n        <tr>\r\n            <td><em>\u0110T Olympic Vi\u1ec7t Nam n\u1eb1m chung b\u1ea3ng v\u1edbi Nh\u1eadt B\u1ea3n t\u1ea1i ASIAD 2018.</em></td>\r\n        </tr>\r\n    </tbody>\r\n</table>\r\n</div>\r\n<p style=\"text-align: justify;\">Minh Long (TTVN)<span class=\"apple-converted-space\"><o:p></o:p></span></p></div><advbottom>","new_url":"","id":"4487","checkdouble":"191785"},{"date":"15:17 22/07","title":"TR\u1ef0C TI\u1ebeP TPHCM vs Qu\u1ea3ng Ninh 19h00 ng\u00e0y 22/7 (V-League 2018)","type":"B\u00f3ng \u0111\u00e1 Vi\u1ec7t Nam","img_url":"https://static.bongda24h.vn/medias/original/2018/7/22/tphcm-vs-quang-ninh-vong-20-vleague-2018.jpg","new_desc":"<link href='https://bongda24h.vn/websites/css/stylemobilev3.css?v=3' rel='stylesheet' type='text/css' /><style>body{margin:0px; padding:3px; font-size: 20px;}*{font-size:20px !important;}.articlerelatepannel { display:none; padding: 6px;  margin-top:5px; margin-bottom:5px; background-color:#f7f7f7; border:solid 1px #0cac0c}.mediaplayercontent{display:none;}h1{font-size:24px; font-weight:bold; color:black;}h2{font-weight:bold; color:black; width:100%; margin-top:5px !important;}h3{font-weight:bold; color:black;}iframe{display:none;}</style><div class='chitiet_tin'><h2>Tr\u1ef1c ti\u1ebfp TPHCM vs Qu\u1ea3ng Ninh: C\u1eadp nh\u1eadt li\u00ean t\u1ee5c di\u1ec5n bi\u1ebfn t\u01b0\u1eddng thu\u1eadt t\u00ecnh hu\u1ed1ng k\u1ebft qu\u1ea3 b\u00f3ng \u0111\u00e1 tr\u1eadn \u0111\u1ea5u TPHCM vs Qu\u1ea3ng Ninh v\u00f2ng 20 gi\u1ea3i v\u00f4 \u0111\u1ecbch qu\u1ed1c gia V\u0110QG Vi\u1ec7t Nam V-League 2018 l\u00fac 19h00 t\u1ed1i ng\u00e0y h\u00f4m nay 22/7.</h2><h2 style=\"text-align: left;\">Tr\u1ef1c ti\u1ebfp TPHCM vs Qu\u1ea3ng Ninh: C\u1eadp nh\u1eadt li\u00ean t\u1ee5c di\u1ec5n bi\u1ebfn t\u01b0\u1eddng thu\u1eadt t\u00ecnh hu\u1ed1ng k\u1ebft qu\u1ea3 b\u00f3ng \u0111\u00e1 tr\u1eadn \u0111\u1ea5u TPHCM vs Qu\u1ea3ng Ninh v\u00f2ng 20 gi\u1ea3i v\u00f4 \u0111\u1ecbch qu\u1ed1c gia V\u0110QG Vi\u1ec7t Nam V-League 2018 l\u00fac 19h00 t\u1ed1i ng\u00e0y h\u00f4m nay 22/7.</h2>\r\n<div style=\"text-align: left;\">Kh\u00f4ng xem \u0111\u01b0\u1ee3c, vui l\u00f2ng click v\u00e0o \u0111\u00e2y <span href=\"https://bongda24h.vn/truc-tiep-bong-da/tran-dau/tphcm-vs-quang-ninh-vong-20-vleague-2018-372-191786.html\" target=\"_blank\"><span style=\"color: rgb(128, 0, 0);\"><u><strong>TR\u1ef0C TI\u1ebeP TPHCM VS QU\u1ea2NG NINH</strong></u></span></span></div></div><advbottom>","new_url":"","id":"4486","checkdouble":"191786"},{"date":"16:59 22/07","title":"Thuy\u1ec1n tr\u01b0\u1edfng PSG n\u00f3ng l\u00f2ng \u0111\u01b0\u1ee3c l\u00e0m vi\u1ec7c v\u1edbi Mbappe","type":"B\u00f3ng \u0111\u00e1 Ph\u00e1p","img_url":"https://static.bongda24h.vn/medias/original/2018/7/22/thuyen-truong-psg-nong-long-duoc-lam-viec-voi-mbappe.jpg","new_desc":"<link href='https://bongda24h.vn/websites/css/stylemobilev3.css?v=3' rel='stylesheet' type='text/css' /><style>body{margin:0px; padding:3px; font-size: 20px;}*{font-size:20px !important;}.articlerelatepannel { display:none; padding: 6px;  margin-top:5px; margin-bottom:5px; background-color:#f7f7f7; border:solid 1px #0cac0c}.mediaplayercontent{display:none;}h1{font-size:24px; font-weight:bold; color:black;}h2{font-weight:bold; color:black; width:100%; margin-top:5px !important;}h3{font-weight:bold; color:black;}iframe{display:none;}</style><div class='chitiet_tin'><h2>M\u1edbi \u0111\u01b0\u1ee3c b\u1ed5 nhi\u1ec7m v\u00e0o chi\u1ebfc gh\u1ebf n\u00f3ng c\u1ee7a PSG, HLV Thomas Tuchel ph\u1ea5n kh\u00edch v\u1ec1 Mbappe \u2013 ng\u00f4i sao v\u00e0 l\u00e0 nh\u00e0 v\u00f4 \u0111\u1ecbch th\u1ebf gi\u1edbi.\r\n</h2><div style=\"text-align: justify;\">&nbsp;</div>\r\n<h2>Tuchel h\u01b0\u1edbng \u0111\u1ebfn m\u00f9a gi\u1ea3i m\u1edbi</h2>\r\n<h2>&nbsp;</h2>\r\n<div style=\"text-align: justify;\">Sau khi ch\u00ednh th\u1ee9c chia tay Unai Emery v\u00ec kh\u00f4ng \u0111\u00e1p \u1ee9ng \u0111\u01b0\u1ee3c k\u1ef3 v\u1ecdng, G\u00e3 nh\u00e0 gi\u00e0u n\u01b0\u1edbc Ph\u00e1p \u0111\u00e3 b\u1ed5 nhi\u1ec7m Thomas Tuchel. Tr\u00ean c\u01b0\u01a1ng v\u1ecb thuy\u1ec1n tr\u01b0\u1edfng PSG, HLV ng\u01b0\u1eddi \u0110\u1ee9c \u0111ang t\u1ecf ra r\u1ea5t h\u00e0o h\u1ee9ng v\u1ec1 vi\u1ec7c \u0111\u01b0\u1ee3c d\u1eabn d\u1eaft nh\u1eefng si\u00eau sao h\u00e0ng \u0111\u1ea7u, ti\u00eau bi\u1ec3u nh\u01b0 sao tr\u1ebb Kylian Mbappe.<br>\r\n&nbsp;</div>\r\n</div><mobileadv><link href='https://bongda24h.vn/websites/css/stylemobilev3.css?v=3' rel='stylesheet' type='text/css' /><style>body{margin:0px; padding:3px; font-size: 20px;}*{font-size:20px !important;}.articlerelatepannel { display:none; padding: 6px;  margin-top:5px; margin-bottom:5px; background-color:#f7f7f7; border:solid 1px #0cac0c}.mediaplayercontent{display:none;}h1{font-size:24px; font-weight:bold; color:black;}h2{font-weight:bold; color:black; width:100%; margin-top:5px !important;}h3{font-weight:bold; color:black;}iframe{display:none;}</style><div class='chitiet_tin'><div style=\"text-align: justify;\">N\u00f3i v\u1ec1 c\u00f4ng vi\u1ec7c c\u1ee7a m\u00ecnh, Tuchel ph\u1ea5n kh\u00edch: &ldquo;Ch\u00fang t\u00f4i \u0111ang s\u1edf h\u1eefu nh\u1eefng ng\u00f4i sao t\u1ea5n c\u00f4ng xu\u1ea5t s\u1eafc nh\u01b0 Kylian, Edinson v\u00e0 Neymar. T\u00f4i kh\u00f4ng th\u1ec3 ch\u1edd \u0111\u1ee3i \u0111\u1ec3 \u0111\u01b0\u1ee3c l\u00e0m vi\u1ec7c v\u1edbi h\u1ecd, nh\u1eefng t\u00e0i n\u0103ng v\u00f4 c\u00f9ng \u0111\u1eb7c bi\u1ec7t. Ch\u00fang ta c\u1ea7n ph\u1ea3i ki\u00ean nh\u1eabn, b\u1edfi h\u1ecd \u0111\u00e3 d\u00e0nh qu\u00e1 nhi\u1ec1u th\u1eddi gian t\u1ea1i World Cup.&rdquo;<br>\r\n&nbsp;</div>\r\n<div style=\"text-align: justify;\">Trong tr\u1eadn \u0111\u1ea5u \u0111\u1ea7u ti\u00ean chu\u1ea9n b\u1ecb cho m\u00f9a gi\u1ea3i m\u1edbi, PSG \u0111\u00e3 th\u1ea5t th\u1ee7 tr\u01b0\u1edbc Bayern Munich v\u1edbi t\u1ef7 s\u1ed1 1-3. Tuchel chia s\u1ebb: &ldquo;T\u00f4i t\u1ef1 h\u00e0o v\u1ec1 nh\u1eefng g\u00ec c\u00e1c c\u1ea7u th\u1ee7 \u0111\u00e3 l\u00e0m \u0111\u01b0\u1ee3c, t\u00f4i kh\u00f4ng tr\u00f4ng ch\u1edd v\u00e0o m\u1ed9t chi\u1ebfn th\u1eafng trong tr\u1eadn n\u00e0y.&rdquo;<br>\r\n<br>\r\n<div style=\"text-align: center; width: 100%\" class=\"imagecontainer\">\r\n<table style=\"text-align: center; width:100%;\">\r\n    <tbody>\r\n        <tr style=\"width:100%;\">\r\n            <td style=\"width: 100%;\" align=\"center\"><img style=\"border: none\" alt=\"Thomas Tuchel ph\u1ea5n kh\u00edch v\u1ec1 Mbappe v\u00e0 Neymar\" title=\"Mbappe v\u00e0 Neymar\" src=\"https://static.bongda24h.vn/medias/mobile/2018/7/22/thuyen-truong-psg-nong-long-duoc-lam-viec-voi-mbappe.jpg\"></td>\r\n        </tr>\r\n        <tr>\r\n            <td>\r\n            <h3>Thomas Tuchel ph\u1ea5n kh\u00edch v\u1ec1 Mbappe v\u00e0 Neymar</h3>\r\n            </td>\r\n        </tr>\r\n    </tbody>\r\n</table>\r\n</div>\r\n<div><br>\r\n&ldquo;Nh\u1eefng c\u1ea7u th\u1ee7 gi\u00e0u kinh nghi\u1ec7m nh\u1ea5t c\u1ee7a ch\u00fang t\u00f4i l\u00e0 Adrien Rabiot, Lassana Diarra, Christopher Nkunku v\u00e0 Gianluigi Buffon, v\u00ec v\u1eady ch\u00fang t\u00f4i kh\u00f4ng hy v\u1ecdng qu\u00e1 nhi\u1ec1u. Ch\u00fang t\u00f4i s\u1ebd c\u1ea7n m\u1ed9t gi\u1ea3i ph\u00e1p n\u01a1i h\u00e0ng ti\u1ec1n v\u1ec7, PSG c\u1ea7n ng\u01b0\u1eddi th\u1ebf ch\u1ed7 Thiago Motta.&rdquo;</div>\r\n<div>&nbsp;</div>\r\n</div>\r\n<div style=\"text-align: justify;\">&ldquo;Anh \u1ea5y kh\u00f4ng ch\u1ec9 l\u00e0 m\u1ed9t c\u1ea7u th\u1ee7 t\u00e0i n\u0103ng, m\u00e0 c\u00f2n l\u00e0 ti\u1ebfng n\u00f3i l\u1edbn trong ph\u00f2ng thay \u0111\u1ed3. K\u1ef3 chuy\u1ec3n nh\u01b0\u1ee3ng v\u1eabn \u0111ang m\u1edf c\u1eeda, v\u00ec v\u1eady ch\u00fang t\u00f4i bi\u1ebft nh\u1eefng g\u00ec ch\u00fang t\u00f4i \u0111ang l\u00e0m. \u0110\u1ed9i b\u00f3ng s\u1ebd xem x\u00e9t nh\u1eefng g\u00ec c\u00f3 th\u1ec3. Adrien Rabiot s\u1ebd c\u00f3 ch\u1ed7 \u0111\u1ee9ng trong \u0111\u1ed9i h\u00ecnh. T\u00f4i th\u00edch l\u00e0m vi\u1ec7c v\u1edbi c\u1eadu \u1ea5y, ti\u1ec1m n\u0103ng c\u1ee7a Adrien l\u00e0 r\u1ea5t l\u1edbn, nh\u01b0ng c\u1eadu \u1ea5y ph\u1ea3i quy\u1ebft \u0111\u1ecbnh c\u00f3 c\u1ea3m th\u1ea5y ph\u00f9 h\u1ee3p v\u1edbi d\u1ef1 \u00e1n c\u1ee7a CLB hay kh\u00f4ng.&rdquo;<br>\r\n&nbsp;</div>\r\n<div style=\"text-align: justify;\">Quay tr\u1edf l\u1ea1i v\u1edbi h\u00e0ng c\u00f4ng, r\u00f5 r\u00e0ng Thomas Tuchel ph\u1ea5n kh\u00edch v\u1ec1 Mbappe, Cavani v\u00e0 Neymar &ndash; b\u1ed9 ba ch\u1ebft ch\u00f3c c\u1ee7a PSG. Nh\u01b0ng \u0111\u1ec3 \u0111\u1ea1t m\u1ee5c ti\u00eau gi\u00e0nh ch\u1ee9c v\u00f4 \u0111\u1ecbch Champions League nh\u01b0 k\u1ef3 v\u1ecdng, t\u00e2n HLV ng\u01b0\u1eddi \u0110\u1ee9c c\u1ea7n c\u00f3 th\u00eam nh\u1eefng s\u1ef1 b\u1ed5 sung \u1edf v\u1ecb tr\u00ed kh\u00e1c.<br>\r\n<br>\r\n<div class=\"articlerelatepannel\">\r\n<div class=\"articlerelate2\"><span href=\"/bong-da-phap/neymar-chang-co-van-de-gi-voi-mbappe-197-191720.html\"><img src=\"https://static.bongda24h.vn/medias/thumnail/2017/10/6/neymar-chang-co-van-de-gi-voi-mbappe.jpg\" alt=\"\"></span><span href=\"/bong-da-phap/neymar-chang-co-van-de-gi-voi-mbappe-197-191720.html\">Neymar ch\u1eb3ng c\u00f3 v\u1ea5n \u0111\u1ec1 g\u00ec v\u1edbi Mbappe</span><br>\r\nM\u1eb7c d\u00f9 tr\u1ea3i qua k\u1ef3 World Cup 2018 v\u1edbi phong \u0111\u1ed9 tr\u00e1i ng\u01b0\u1ee3c, nh\u01b0ng Neymar kh\u00f4ng c\u00f3 v\u1ea5n \u0111\u1ec1 g\u00ec v\u1edbi Mbappe &ndash; \u0111\u00f3 l\u00e0 l\u1eddi kh\u1eb3ng \u0111\u1ecbnh m\u1edbi nh\u1ea5t c\u1ee7a Ch\u1ee7 t\u1ecbch PSG.</div>\r\n<div class=\"articlerelate2\"><span href=\"/world-cup-2018/kylian-mbappe-mon-qua-duoc-ban-tang-cho-bong-da-421-191618.html\"><img src=\"https://static.bongda24h.vn/medias/thumnail/2018/7/16/kylian-mbappe-mon-qua-duoc-ban-tang-cho-bong-da.jpg\" alt=\"\"></span><span href=\"/world-cup-2018/kylian-mbappe-mon-qua-duoc-ban-tang-cho-bong-da-421-191618.html\">Kylian Mbappe: M\u00f3n qu\u00e0 \u0111\u01b0\u1ee3c ban t\u1eb7ng cho b\u00f3ng \u0111\u00e1</span><br>\r\nC\u0169ng ph\u1ea3i \u0111\u1ebfn l\u00fac th\u00f4i, k\u1ef7 nguy\u00ean th\u1ed1ng tr\u1ecb c\u1ee7a Lionel Messi v\u00e0 Cristiano Ronaldo c\u1ea7n m\u1ed9t k\u1ebb th\u00e1ch th\u1ee9c, ai \u0111\u00f3 l\u00e0 m\u00f3n qu\u00e0 th\u1ef1c s\u1ef1 \u0111\u01b0\u1ee3c Th\u01b0\u1ee3ng \u0110\u1ebf ban t\u1eb7ng cho...</div>\r\n</div>\r\n</div>\r\n<div style=\"text-align: justify;\">Nguy\u1ec7t Anh (TTVN)</div></div><advbottom>","new_url":"","id":"4485","checkdouble":"191791"},{"date":"15:11 22/07","title":"T\u1edbi Barca, t\u00e2n binh 36 tri\u1ec7u Euro h\u1ea1nh ph\u00fac b\u1edfi \u0111i\u1ec1u g\u00ec?","type":"B\u00f3ng \u0111\u00e1 TBN","img_url":"https://static.bongda24h.vn/medias/thumnail/2018/7/22/lenglet-phat-bieu-sau-khi-toi-barca.jpg","new_desc":"<link href='https://bongda24h.vn/websites/css/stylemobilev3.css?v=3' rel='stylesheet' type='text/css' /><style>body{margin:0px; padding:3px; font-size: 20px;}*{font-size:20px !important;}.articlerelatepannel { display:none; padding: 6px;  margin-top:5px; margin-bottom:5px; background-color:#f7f7f7; border:solid 1px #0cac0c}.mediaplayercontent{display:none;}h1{font-size:24px; font-weight:bold; color:black;}h2{font-weight:bold; color:black; width:100%; margin-top:5px !important;}h3{font-weight:bold; color:black;}iframe{display:none;}</style><div class='chitiet_tin'><h2>Clement Lenglet ph\u00e1t bi\u1ec3u sau khi t\u1edbi Barca. Trung v\u1ec7 23 tu\u1ed5i kh\u1eb3ng \u0111\u1ecbnh r\u1ea5t vui v\u00ec t\u1eeb gi\u1edd kh\u00f4ng c\u00f2n ph\u1ea3i \u0111\u1ed1i m\u1eb7t v\u1edbi Lionel Messi v\u00e0 nh\u1eefng ng\u00f4i sao c\u1ee7a Blaugrana.</h2><div style=\"text-align: justify;\">\u00a0</div>\r\n<h2>Lenglet gia nh\u1eadp Barca</h2>\r\n</div><mobileadv><link href='https://bongda24h.vn/websites/css/stylemobilev3.css?v=3' rel='stylesheet' type='text/css' /><style>body{margin:0px; padding:3px; font-size: 20px;}*{font-size:20px !important;}.articlerelatepannel { display:none; padding: 6px;  margin-top:5px; margin-bottom:5px; background-color:#f7f7f7; border:solid 1px #0cac0c}.mediaplayercontent{display:none;}h1{font-size:24px; font-weight:bold; color:black;}h2{font-weight:bold; color:black; width:100%; margin-top:5px !important;}h3{font-weight:bold; color:black;}iframe{display:none;}</style><div class='chitiet_tin'><div style=\"text-align: justify;\"><br>\r\nH\u1ed3i \u0111\u1ea7u th\u00e1ng n\u00e0y, Clement Lenglet \u0111\u00e3 k\u00fd h\u1ee3p \u0111\u1ed3ng gia nh\u1eadp Barcelona v\u1edbi gi\u00e1 36 tri\u1ec7u Euro t\u1eeb Sevilla. V\u1edbi vi\u1ec7c nh\u1eefng Yerry Mina hay Thomas Vermaelen g\u00e2y th\u1ea5t v\u1ecdng khi ra s\u00e2n, \u0111\u1ed9i ch\u1ee7 s\u00e2n Camp Nou nh\u1eafm t\u1edbi trung v\u1ec7 tr\u1ebb ng\u01b0\u1eddi Ph\u00e1p.<br>\r\n<br>\r\nLenglet gia nh\u1eadp Sevilla \u0111\u1ea7u n\u0103m 2017 t\u1eeb Nancy v\u1edbi gi\u00e1 ch\u1ec9 5 tri\u1ec7u Euro. 1 n\u0103m r\u01b0\u1ee1i tr\u00f4i qua, gi\u00e1 c\u1ee7a anh \u0111\u00e3 t\u0103ng l\u00ean h\u01a1n 7 l\u1ea7n v\u00e0 v\u1ecb th\u1ebf trong l\u00e0ng b\u00f3ng \u0111\u00e1 c\u0169ng kh\u00e1c. Lenglet gi\u1edd l\u00e0 m\u1ed9t trong nh\u1eefng c\u1ea7u th\u1ee7 tr\u1ebb gi\u00e0u tri\u1ec3n v\u1ecdng nh\u1ea5t t\u1ea1i ch\u00e2u \u00c2u.<br>\r\n<br>\r\n<div style=\"text-align: center; width: 100%\" class=\"imagecontainer\">\r\n<table style=\"text-align: center; width:100%;\">\r\n    <tbody>\r\n        <tr style=\"width:100%;\">\r\n            <td style=\"width:100%; text-align: center;\" align=\"center\"><img style=\"border: none\" alt=\"Clement Lenglet ph\u00e1t bi\u1ec3u sau khi t\u1edbi Barca h\u00ecnh \u1ea3nh\" title=\"Clement Lenglet ph\u00e1t bi\u1ec3u sau khi t\u1edbi Barca h\u00ecnh \u1ea3nh\" src=\"https://static.bongda24h.vn/medias/mobile/2018/6/9/Clement-Lenglet-phat-bieu-sau-khi-toi-Barca-hinh-anh.jpg\"></td>\r\n        </tr>\r\n        <tr>\r\n            <td style=\"text-align: center\">Lenglet gia nh\u1eadp Barca t\u1eeb Sevilla</td>\r\n        </tr>\r\n    </tbody>\r\n</table>\r\n</div>\r\n<br>\r\nLenglet ti\u1ebfp b\u01b0\u1edbc nh\u1eefng Dani Alves, Seydou Keita v\u00e0 Adriano chuy\u1ec3n t\u1eeb Sevilla t\u1edbi Barca trong nh\u1eefng n\u0103m qua. Tr\u01b0\u1edbc m\u1eaft, anh s\u1ebd l\u00e0 s\u1ef1 d\u1ef1 ph\u00f2ng ch\u1ea5t l\u01b0\u1ee3ng cho b\u1ed9 \u0111\u00f4i trung v\u1ec7 Gerard Pique v\u00e0 Samuel Umtiti.<br>\r\n\u00a0</div>\r\n<h2>H\u1ea1nh ph\u00fac v\u00ec m\u1ed9t \u0111i\u1ec1u</h2>\r\n<div style=\"text-align: justify;\"><br>\r\nTrong ng\u00e0y ra m\u1eaft Barca, Lenglet b\u00e0y t\u1ecf ni\u1ec1m vui khi \u0111\u01b0\u1ee3c ch\u01a1i b\u00f3ng c\u00f9ng v\u1edbi nh\u1eefng ng\u00f4i sao t\u1ea1i CLB, \u0111\u1eb7c bi\u1ec7t l\u00e0 Lionel Messi. \u201cT\u00f4i th\u1ef1c s\u1ef1 h\u1ea1nh ph\u00fac khi \u0111\u01b0\u1ee3c \u1edf \u0111\u00e2y, b\u1edfi t\u00f4i kh\u00f4ng ph\u1ea3i \u0111\u1ed1i m\u1eb7t v\u1edbi h\u1ecd\u201d, Lenglet ph\u00e1t bi\u1ec3u sau khi t\u1edbi Barca m\u1ed9t c\u00e1ch vui v\u1ebb.<br>\r\n<br>\r\n<div style=\"text-align: center; width: 100%\" class=\"imagecontainer\">\r\n<table style=\"text-align: center; width:100%;\">\r\n    <tbody>\r\n        <tr style=\"width:100%;\">\r\n            <td style=\"width:100%; text-align: center;\" align=\"center\"><img style=\"border: none\" alt=\"trung ve Lenglet\" title=\"trung ve Lenglet\" src=\"https://static.bongda24h.vn/medias/mobile/2018/7/22/lenglet-phat-bieu-sau-khi-toi-barca.jpg\"></td>\r\n        </tr>\r\n        <tr>\r\n            <td style=\"text-align: center\">\r\n            <h3>Lenglet ph\u00e1t bi\u1ec3u sau khi t\u1edbi Barca r\u1eb1ng h\u1ea1nh ph\u00fac l\u00e0 \u0111\u1ed3ng \u0111\u1ed9i c\u1ee7a Messi</h3>\r\n            </td>\r\n        </tr>\r\n    </tbody>\r\n</table>\r\n</div>\r\n<br>\r\n\u201cMessi l\u00e0 c\u1ea7u th\u1ee7 hay nh\u1ea5t th\u1ebf gi\u1edbi. Anh \u1ea5y d\u1ec5 d\u00e0ng th\u1ed1ng tr\u1ecb c\u00e1c tr\u1eadn \u0111\u1ea5u v\u00e0 c\u00f3 th\u1ec3 ghi b\u00e0n b\u1ea5t c\u1ee9 l\u00fac n\u00e0o \u1edf b\u1ea5t c\u1ee9 kho\u1ea3ng c\u00e1ch n\u00e0o. N\u1ebfu b\u1ea1n g\u1eb7p may, thi tho\u1ea3ng b\u1ea1n c\u00f3 th\u1ec3 ng\u0103n ch\u1eb7n Messi, nh\u01b0ng m\u1ed9t ng\u01b0\u1eddi kh\u00e1c c\u00f3 th\u1ec3 gieo s\u1ea7u cho b\u1ea1n.\u201d<br>\r\n<br>\r\nLenglet hy v\u1ecdng c\u00f3 th\u1ec3 s\u1edbm th\u00edch nghi v\u1edbi cu\u1ed9c s\u1ed1ng \u1edf Barca. Anh tin r\u1eb1ng s\u1ebd \u0111\u01b0\u1ee3c n\u00e2ng t\u1ea7m h\u01a1n n\u1eefa t\u1ea1i \u0111\u00e2y. \u201cKhi b\u1ea1n ch\u01a1i v\u1edbi nh\u1eefng c\u1ea7u th\u1ee7 gi\u1ecfi, s\u1ef1 th\u00edch nghi s\u1ebd d\u1ec5 d\u00e0ng h\u01a1n m\u1ed9t ch\u00fat. \u1ede \u0111\u00e2y, t\u1ea5t c\u1ea3 c\u00e1c c\u1ea7u th\u1ee7 \u0111\u1ec1u \u1edf \u0111\u1eb3ng c\u1ea5p cao nh\u1ea5t\u201d, c\u1ea7u th\u1ee7 sinh n\u0103m 1995 n\u00f3i th\u00eam.<br>\r\n<br>\r\n\u201cTri\u1ebft l\u00fd c\u1ee7a Barca l\u00e0 tri\u1ec3n khai b\u00f3ng t\u1eeb h\u00e0ng th\u1ee7 v\u00e0 \u0111\u00f3 l\u00e0 CLB duy nh\u1ea5t tr\u00ean th\u1ebf gi\u1edbi ch\u01a1i v\u1edbi phong c\u00e1ch n\u00e0y. M\u1ecdi ng\u01b0\u1eddi \u0111\u1ec1u n\u00f3i v\u1edbi t\u00f4i r\u1eb1ng Barcelona l\u00e0 th\u00e0nh ph\u1ed1 \u0111\u00e1ng kinh ng\u1ea1c th\u1ebf n\u00e0o, v\u00e0 khi t\u1edbi \u0111\u00e2y b\u1ea1n kh\u00f4ng bao gi\u1edd mu\u1ed1n ra \u0111i.\u201d<br>\r\n<strong><br>\r\nXem th\u00eam m\u1ed9t s\u1ed1 b\u00e0i vi\u1ebft v\u1ec1 chuy\u1ec3n nh\u01b0\u1ee3ng Barca tr\u00ean Bongda24h.vn:<br>\r\n<br>\r\n<div class=\"articlerelatepannel\">\r\n<div class=\"articlerelate\"><span href=\"/bong-da-anh/everton-muon-mua-digne-gia-22-trieu-bang-172-191729.html\">\u201cH\u00e0ng th\u1ea3i\u201d Barca \u0111\u01b0\u1ee3c h\u1ecfi mua v\u1edbi gi\u00e1 h\u1ea5p d\u1eabn</span></div>\r\n<div class=\"articlerelate\"><span href=\"/bong-da-anh/keita-toi-tu-choi-bayern-va-barca-de-den-liverpool-172-191715.html\">Keita: T\u00f4i t\u1eeb ch\u1ed1i Bayern v\u00e0 Barca \u0111\u1ec3 \u0111\u1ebfn Liverpool</span></div>\r\n<div class=\"articlerelate\"><span href=\"/tin-chuyen-nhuong/gui-de-nghi-lan-3-barca-quyet-mua-ngoi-sao-cua-chelsea-187-191704.html\">G\u1eedi \u0111\u1ec1 ngh\u1ecb l\u1ea7n 3, Barca quy\u1ebft mua ng\u00f4i sao c\u1ee7a Chelsea</span></div>\r\n<div class=\"articlerelate\"><span href=\"/bong-da-anh/chelsea-quan-tam-toi-jasper-cillessen-172-191681.html\">S\u1ee3 Real 'c\u01b0\u1edbp' ng\u01b0\u1eddi, Chelsea v\u1ed9i v\u00e3 h\u1ecfi mua sao Barca</span></div>\r\n<div class=\"articlerelate\"><span href=\"/bong-da-anh/lucas-digne-chuan-bi-cap-ben-ngoai-hang-anh-172-191654.html\">H\u00e0ng th\u1ea3i Barca chu\u1ea9n b\u1ecb c\u1eadp b\u1ebfn Ngo\u1ea1i h\u1ea1ng Anh</span></div>\r\n</div>\r\n<br>\r\n<br>\r\n\u00dd An (TTVN)</strong><br>\r\n\u00a0</div></div><advbottom>","new_url":"","id":"4484","checkdouble":"191783"},{"date":"16:34 22/07","title":"T\u00e2n binh c\u1ee7a Barca th\u1edf ph\u00e0o v\u00ec kh\u00f4ng c\u00f2n ph\u1ea3i s\u1ee3 Messi","type":"B\u00f3ng \u0111\u00e1 TBN","img_url":"https://static.bongda24h.vn/medias/original/2018/7/22/tan-binh-cua-barca-tho-phao-vi-khong-con-phai-so-messi.jpg","new_desc":"<link href='https://bongda24h.vn/websites/css/stylemobilev3.css?v=3' rel='stylesheet' type='text/css' /><style>body{margin:0px; padding:3px; font-size: 20px;}*{font-size:20px !important;}.articlerelatepannel { display:none; padding: 6px;  margin-top:5px; margin-bottom:5px; background-color:#f7f7f7; border:solid 1px #0cac0c}.mediaplayercontent{display:none;}h1{font-size:24px; font-weight:bold; color:black;}h2{font-weight:bold; color:black; width:100%; margin-top:5px !important;}h3{font-weight:bold; color:black;}iframe{display:none;}</style><div class='chitiet_tin'><h2>Trung v\u1ec7 m\u1edbi gia nh\u1eadp Barca t\u1eeb Sevilla, Clement Lenglet chia s\u1ebb v\u1ec1 Messi v\u1edbi s\u1ef1 t\u00f4n tr\u1ecdng r\u1ea5t l\u1edbn.\r\n</h2><h2><br>\r\nLenglet th\u1edf ph\u00e0o v\u00ec Messi<br>\r\n&nbsp;</h2>\r\n<div style=\"text-align: justify;\">El Pulga l\u00e0 n\u1ed7i kinh ho\u00e0ng \u0111\u1ed1i v\u1edbi b\u1ea5t k\u1ef3 h\u1eadu v\u1ec7 n\u00e0o \u1edf La Liga. Nh\u01b0ng \u0111\u1ed1i v\u1edbi Clement Lenglet &ndash; trung v\u1ec7 tr\u1ebb ng\u01b0\u1eddi Ph\u00e1p, \u0111i\u1ec1u n\u00e0y kh\u00f4ng c\u00f2n l\u00e0 v\u1ea5n \u0111\u1ec1 n\u1eefa. B\u1edfi anh \u0111\u00e3 tr\u1edf th\u00e0nh \u0111\u1ed3ng \u0111\u1ed9i c\u1ee7a Messi sau khi Barca ch\u1ea5p nh\u1eadn chi ra s\u1ed1 ti\u1ec1n gi\u1ea3i ph\u00f3ng h\u1ee3p \u0111\u1ed3ng.<br>\r\n&nbsp;</div>\r\n<div style=\"text-align: justify;\">Chia s\u1ebb v\u1ec1 ni\u1ec1m h\u1ea1nh ph\u00fac khi gia nh\u1eadp G\u00e3 kh\u1ed5ng l\u1ed3 x\u1ee9 Catalonia, c\u1ea7u th\u1ee7 23 tu\u1ed5i cho bi\u1ebft: &ldquo;Th\u1eadt vui m\u1eebng khi \u0111\u01b0\u1ee3c c\u00f3 m\u1eb7t t\u1ea1i \u0111\u00e2y, b\u1edfi t\u00f4i kh\u00f4ng c\u00f2n ph\u1ea3i \u0111\u1ed1i m\u1eb7t v\u1edbi Barca n\u1eefa. Messi l\u00e0 c\u1ea7u th\u1ee7 xu\u1ea5t s\u1eafc nh\u1ea5t th\u1ebf gi\u1edbi. Anh \u1ea5y th\u1ed1ng tr\u1ecb tr\u1eadn \u0111\u1ea5u qu\u00e1 d\u1ec5 d\u00e0ng, v\u00e0 ghi b\u00e0n b\u1ea5t c\u1ee9 l\u00fac n\u00e0o anh \u1ea5y th\u00edch.&rdquo;<br>\r\n&nbsp;</div>\r\n</div><mobileadv><link href='https://bongda24h.vn/websites/css/stylemobilev3.css?v=3' rel='stylesheet' type='text/css' /><style>body{margin:0px; padding:3px; font-size: 20px;}*{font-size:20px !important;}.articlerelatepannel { display:none; padding: 6px;  margin-top:5px; margin-bottom:5px; background-color:#f7f7f7; border:solid 1px #0cac0c}.mediaplayercontent{display:none;}h1{font-size:24px; font-weight:bold; color:black;}h2{font-weight:bold; color:black; width:100%; margin-top:5px !important;}h3{font-weight:bold; color:black;}iframe{display:none;}</style><div class='chitiet_tin'><div style=\"text-align: justify;\">&ldquo;N\u1ebfu g\u1eb7p may, b\u1ea1n c\u00f3 th\u1ec3 ng\u0103n ch\u1eb7n anh \u1ea5y m\u1ed9t l\u00fac, nh\u01b0ng r\u1ed3i sau \u0111\u00f3 s\u1ebd c\u00f3 ng\u01b0\u1eddi t\u1ea5n c\u00f4ng v\u00e0o v\u1ecb tr\u00ed c\u1ee7a b\u1ea1n. Khi b\u1ea1n ch\u01a1i b\u00ean c\u1ea1nh nh\u1eefng ng\u01b0\u1eddi \u0111\u1ed3ng \u0111\u1ed9i gi\u1ecfi, s\u1ef1 th\u00edch nghi s\u1ebd tr\u1edf n\u00ean d\u1ec5 d\u00e0ng h\u01a1n. T\u1ea1i Barca, t\u1ea5t c\u1ea3 c\u00e1c c\u1ea7u th\u1ee7 \u0111\u1ec1u ch\u01a1i b\u00f3ng \u1edf \u0111\u1eb3ng c\u1ea5p cao nh\u1ea5t.&rdquo;<br>\r\n<br>\r\n<div style=\"text-align: center; width: 100%\" class=\"imagecontainer\">\r\n<table style=\"text-align: center; width:100%;\">\r\n    <tbody>\r\n        <tr style=\"width:100%;\">\r\n            <td style=\"width: 100%;\" align=\"center\"><img style=\"border: none\" alt=\"Clement Lenglet chia s\u1ebb v\u1ec1 Messi\" title=\"Lenglet chia s\u1ebb v\u1ec1 Messi\" src=\"https://static.bongda24h.vn/medias/mobile/2018/7/22/tan-binh-cua-barca-tho-phao-vi-khong-con-phai-so-messi.jpg\"></td>\r\n        </tr>\r\n        <tr>\r\n            <td>\r\n            <h3>Clement Lenglet chia s\u1ebb v\u1ec1 Messi</h3>\r\n            </td>\r\n        </tr>\r\n    </tbody>\r\n</table>\r\n</div>\r\n</div>\r\n<div style=\"text-align: justify;\"><br>\r\n&ldquo;Tri\u1ebft l\u00fd c\u1ee7a Barca l\u00e0 \u0111em qu\u1ea3 b\u00f3ng l\u00ean t\u1eeb tuy\u1ebfn d\u01b0\u1edbi, v\u00e0 \u0111\u00e2y l\u00e0 CLB duy nh\u1ea5t tr\u00ean th\u1ebf gi\u1edbi ch\u01a1i theo c\u00e1ch n\u00e0y. M\u1ecdi ng\u01b0\u1eddi \u0111\u1ec1u n\u00f3i v\u1edbi t\u00f4i v\u1ec1 gi\u1ea5c m\u01a1, nh\u1eefng \u0111i\u1ec1u \u0111\u1eb7c bi\u1ec7t khi gia nh\u1eadp Barca. V\u00e0 m\u1ed9t khi c\u00f3 m\u1eb7t t\u1ea1i \u0111\u00e2y, r\u00f5 r\u00e0ng l\u00e0 b\u1ea1n kh\u00f4ng mu\u1ed1n \u0111i \u0111\u00e2u h\u1ebft&rdquo; &ndash; Clement Lenglet h\u1ebft l\u1eddi ca ng\u1ee3i \u0111\u1ed9i b\u00f3ng m\u1edbi.<br>\r\n&nbsp;</div>\r\n<div style=\"text-align: justify;\">V\u1edbi vi\u1ec7c gia nh\u1eadp \u0111\u1ed9i b\u00f3ng v\u1edbi m\u1ee9c gi\u00e1 36 tri\u1ec7u b\u1ea3ng, trung v\u1ec7 Lenglet l\u00e0 c\u1ea7u th\u1ee7 ti\u1ebfp theo c\u1ee7a Sevilla chuy\u1ec3n \u0111\u1ebfn Barca &ndash; sau nh\u1eefng Dani Alves, Seydou Keita v\u00e0 Adriano. Anh s\u1ebd l\u00e0 s\u1ef1 l\u1ef1a ch\u1ecdn t\u1ed1t \u0111\u1ec3 thay th\u1ebf nh\u1eefng Gerard Pique, Samuel Umtiti ho\u1eb7c Thomas Vermaelen \u1edf h\u00e0ng ph\u00f2ng ng\u1ef1.<br>\r\n&nbsp;</div>\r\n<div style=\"text-align: justify;\">V\u1edbi vi\u1ec7c Clement Lenglet chia s\u1ebb v\u1ec1 Messi b\u1eb1ng nh\u1eefng l\u1eddi khen ng\u1ee3i, c\u00f3 l\u1ebd anh s\u1ebd kh\u00f4ng g\u1eb7p kh\u00f3 kh\u0103n \u0111\u1ec3 th\u00edch nghi t\u1ea1i \u0111\u1ed9i b\u00f3ng m\u1edbi. B\u00ean c\u1ea1nh \u0111\u00f3, nhi\u1ec1u kh\u1ea3 n\u0103ng Barca s\u1ebd \u0111\u1ea9y trung v\u1ec7 tr\u1ebb thi \u0111\u1ea5u r\u1ea5t t\u1ed1t t\u1ea1i World Cup 2018 l\u00e0 Yerry Mina ra \u0111i.<br>\r\n<br>\r\n<div class=\"articlerelatepannel\">\r\n<div class=\"articlerelate2\"><span href=\"/bong-da-tbn/nguoi-hung-colombia-quyet-tam-bam-tru-tai-barca-180-191745.html\"><img src=\"https://static.bongda24h.vn/medias/thumnail/2018/7/21/nguoi-hung-colombia-quyet-tam-bam-tru-tai-barca.jpg\" alt=\"\"></span><span href=\"/bong-da-tbn/nguoi-hung-colombia-quyet-tam-bam-tru-tai-barca-180-191745.html\">Ng\u01b0\u1eddi h\u00f9ng Colombia quy\u1ebft t\u00e2m b\u00e1m tr\u1ee5 t\u1ea1i Barca</span><br>\r\n\u0110\u01b0\u1ee3c li\u00ean h\u1ec7 \u0111\u1ec3 chuy\u1ec3n t\u1edbi Premier League, nh\u01b0ng trung v\u1ec7 Yerry Mina quy\u1ebft \u1edf l\u1ea1i Barca \u0111\u1ec3 ch\u1ee9ng t\u1ecf t\u00e0i n\u0103ng c\u1ee7a m\u00ecnh.</div>\r\n<div class=\"articlerelate2\"><span href=\"/bong-da-anh/keita-toi-tu-choi-bayern-va-barca-de-den-liverpool-172-191715.html\"><img src=\"https://static.bongda24h.vn/medias/thumnail/2018/7/21/keita-toi-tu-choi-bayern-va-barca-de-den-liverpool.jpg\" alt=\"\"></span><span href=\"/bong-da-anh/keita-toi-tu-choi-bayern-va-barca-de-den-liverpool-172-191715.html\">Keita: T\u00f4i t\u1eeb ch\u1ed1i Bayern v\u00e0 Barca \u0111\u1ec3 \u0111\u1ebfn Liverpool</span><br>\r\nTi\u1ec1n v\u1ec7 Naby Keita kh\u1eb3ng \u0111\u1ecbnh anh \u0111\u00e3 t\u1eeb ch\u1ed1i nh\u1eefng \u0111\u1ed9i b\u00f3ng h\u00e0ng \u0111\u1ea7u nh\u01b0 Barcelona hay Bayern Munich \u0111\u1ec3 c\u1eadp b\u1ebfn Liverpool.</div>\r\n</div>\r\n</div>\r\n<div style=\"text-align: justify;\">Nguy\u1ec7t Anh (TTVN)</div></div><advbottom>","new_url":"","id":"4483","checkdouble":"191789"},{"date":"14:48 22/07","title":"C\u00f4ng th\u1ea7n s\u1eb5n s\u00e0ng r\u1eddi Man City \u0111\u1ec3 c\u1ee9u v\u00e3n s\u1ef1 nghi\u1ec7p","type":"B\u00f3ng \u0111\u00e1 Anh","img_url":"https://static.bongda24h.vn/medias/thumnail/2018/7/22/hart-muon-roi-man-city-de-cuu-van-su-nghiep.jpg","new_desc":"<link href='https://bongda24h.vn/websites/css/stylemobilev3.css?v=3' rel='stylesheet' type='text/css' /><style>body{margin:0px; padding:3px; font-size: 20px;}*{font-size:20px !important;}.articlerelatepannel { display:none; padding: 6px;  margin-top:5px; margin-bottom:5px; background-color:#f7f7f7; border:solid 1px #0cac0c}.mediaplayercontent{display:none;}h1{font-size:24px; font-weight:bold; color:black;}h2{font-weight:bold; color:black; width:100%; margin-top:5px !important;}h3{font-weight:bold; color:black;}iframe{display:none;}</style><div class='chitiet_tin'><h2>Joe Hart mu\u1ed1n r\u1eddi Man City \u0111\u1ec3 c\u1ee9u v\u00e3n s\u1ef1 nghi\u1ec7p. Th\u1ee7 th\u00e0nh 31 tu\u1ed5i m\u1edbi tr\u1edf l\u1ea1i N\u1eeda xanh th\u00e0nh Manchester sau qu\u00e3ng th\u1eddi gian cho m\u01b0\u1ee3n th\u1ea5t b\u1ea1i t\u1ea1i Torino v\u00e0 West Ham.</h2><div style=\"text-align: justify;\">\u00a0</div>\r\n<h2>Hart mi\u1ec5n c\u01b0\u1ee1ng tr\u1edf l\u1ea1i Man City</h2>\r\n</div><mobileadv><link href='https://bongda24h.vn/websites/css/stylemobilev3.css?v=3' rel='stylesheet' type='text/css' /><style>body{margin:0px; padding:3px; font-size: 20px;}*{font-size:20px !important;}.articlerelatepannel { display:none; padding: 6px;  margin-top:5px; margin-bottom:5px; background-color:#f7f7f7; border:solid 1px #0cac0c}.mediaplayercontent{display:none;}h1{font-size:24px; font-weight:bold; color:black;}h2{font-weight:bold; color:black; width:100%; margin-top:5px !important;}h3{font-weight:bold; color:black;}iframe{display:none;}</style><div class='chitiet_tin'><div style=\"text-align: justify;\"><br>\r\nJoe Hart gia nh\u1eadp Man City n\u0103m 2006 t\u1eeb CLB qu\u00ea nh\u00e0 Shrewsbury Town. Anh t\u1eebng l\u00e0 tr\u1ee5 c\u1ed9t trong \u0111\u1ed9i h\u00ecnh The Citizens gi\u00e0nh 2 ch\u1ee9c v\u00f4 \u0111\u1ecbch Premier League, 1 c\u00fap FA v\u00e0 2 c\u00fap Li\u00ean \u0111o\u00e0n.<br>\r\n<br>\r\nNh\u01b0ng k\u1ec3 t\u1eeb sau khi HLV Pep Guardiola l\u00ean ti\u1ebfp qu\u1ea3n Man City \u0111\u1ea7u m\u00f9a 2016/17, Hart kh\u00f4ng c\u00f2n ch\u1ed7 \u0111\u1ee9ng. Nh\u00e0 c\u1ea7m qu\u00e2n ng\u01b0\u1eddi T\u00e2y Ban Nha c\u1ea7n m\u1ed9t th\u1ee7 th\u00e0nh bi\u1ebft d\u00f9ng ch\u00e2n ph\u00e2n ph\u1ed1i b\u00f3ng \u1edf ph\u00eda sau v\u00e0 \u0111\u00f3 kh\u00f4ng ph\u1ea3i l\u00e0 phong c\u00e1ch s\u1edf tr\u01b0\u1eddng c\u1ee7a c\u00f4ng th\u1ea7n Man xanh.<br>\r\n<br>\r\n<div style=\"text-align: center; width: 100%\" class=\"imagecontainer\">\r\n<table style=\"text-align: center; width:100%;\">\r\n    <tbody>\r\n        <tr style=\"width:100%;\">\r\n            <td style=\"width:100%; text-align: center;\" align=\"center\"><img style=\"border: none\" alt=\"Joe Hart mu\u1ed1n r\u1eddi Man City \u0111\u1ec3 c\u1ee9u v\u00e3n s\u1ef1 nghi\u1ec7p h\u00ecnh \u1ea3nh\" title=\"Joe Hart mu\u1ed1n r\u1eddi Man City \u0111\u1ec3 c\u1ee9u v\u00e3n s\u1ef1 nghi\u1ec7p h\u00ecnh \u1ea3nh\" src=\"https://static.bongda24h.vn/medias/mobile/2018/4/17/Joe-Hart-muon-roi-Man-City-de-cuu-van-su-nghiep-hinh-anh.PNG\"></td>\r\n        </tr>\r\n        <tr>\r\n            <td style=\"text-align: center\">Joe Hart kh\u00f4ng th\u1ec3 hi\u1ec7n \u0111\u01b0\u1ee3c nhi\u1ec1u t\u1ea1i West Ham</td>\r\n        </tr>\r\n    </tbody>\r\n</table>\r\n</div>\r\n<br>\r\nHart b\u1ecb \u0111\u1ea9y l\u1ea7n l\u01b0\u1ee3t sang Torino v\u00e0 West Ham d\u01b0\u1edbi d\u1ea1ng cho m\u01b0\u1ee3n song \u0111\u1ec1u kh\u00f4ng t\u00e1i hi\u1ec7n \u0111\u01b0\u1ee3c phong \u0111\u1ed9 th\u1eddi \u0111\u1ec9nh cao. H\u1ebft m\u00f9a 2017/18, West Ham quy\u1ebft \u0111\u1ecbnh kh\u00f4ng mua \u0111\u1ee9t v\u00e0 bu\u1ed9c c\u1ea7u th\u1ee7 31 tu\u1ed5i ph\u1ea3i quay l\u1ea1i s\u00e2n Etihad.<br>\r\n\u00a0</div>\r\n<h2>Ch\u01b0a b\u1ecf \u00fd \u0111\u1ecbnh ra \u0111i</h2>\r\n<div style=\"text-align: justify;\"><br>\r\nJoe Hart c\u0169ng c\u00f3 t\u00ean trong danh s\u00e1ch sang M\u1ef9 du \u0111\u1ea5u c\u1ee7a Man City h\u00e8 n\u00e0y. Anh m\u1edbi c\u00f3 l\u1ea7n ra s\u00e2n \u0111\u1ea7u ti\u00ean cho The Citizens t\u1eeb n\u0103m 2016 trong tr\u1eadn giao h\u1eefu v\u1edbi Borussia Dortmund khi v\u00e0o s\u00e2n thay Claudio Bravo \u0111\u1ea7u hi\u1ec7p 2.<br>\r\n<br>\r\n<div style=\"text-align: center; width: 100%\" class=\"imagecontainer\">\r\n<table style=\"text-align: center; width:100%;\">\r\n    <tbody>\r\n        <tr style=\"width:100%;\">\r\n            <td style=\"width:100%; text-align: center;\" align=\"center\"><img style=\"border: none\" alt=\"thu mon Hart\" title=\"thu mon Hart\" src=\"https://static.bongda24h.vn/medias/mobile/2018/7/22/hart-muon-roi-man-city-de-cuu-van-su-nghiep.jpg\"></td>\r\n        </tr>\r\n        <tr>\r\n            <td style=\"text-align: center\">Hart mu\u1ed1n r\u1eddi Man City \u0111\u1ec3 c\u1ee9u v\u00e3n s\u1ef1 nghi\u1ec7p</td>\r\n        </tr>\r\n    </tbody>\r\n</table>\r\n</div>\r\n<br>\r\nD\u00f9 v\u1eady, \u00fd \u0111\u1ecbnh c\u1ee7a Joe Hart mu\u1ed1n r\u1eddi Man City \u0111\u1ec3 c\u1ee9u v\u00e3n s\u1ef1 nghi\u1ec7p v\u1eabn c\u00f2n nguy\u00ean. \u201cT\u00f4i mu\u1ed1n \u0111\u01b0\u1ee3c thi \u0111\u1ea5u l\u00e2u d\u00e0i cho m\u1ed9t CLB, t\u00f4i ngh\u0129 \u0111\u00f3 l\u00e0 \u0111i\u1ec1u hi\u1ec3n nhi\u00ean\u201d, anh n\u00f3i. \u201cT\u00f4i \u0111\u00e3 l\u00e0m nh\u1eefng g\u00ec t\u00f4i c\u00f3 th\u1ec3 trong 2 m\u00f9a gi\u1ea3i qua b\u1edfi c\u1ea7n \u0111\u01b0\u1ee3c d\u1ef1 World Cup, t\u00ecm l\u1ea1i v\u1ecb th\u1ebf c\u1ee7a m\u00ecnh.\u201d<br>\r\n<br>\r\n\u201cT\u00f4i \u0111\u00e3 c\u00f3 kinh nghi\u1ec7m. T\u00f4i \u0111\u00e3 ch\u01a1i \u1edf \u0111\u1eb3ng c\u1ea5p cao nh\u1ea5t trong m\u1ed9t th\u1eddi gian d\u00e0i v\u00e0 th\u1ec3 hi\u1ec7n r\u1ea5t nhi\u1ec1u trong c\u00e1c tr\u1eadn \u0111\u1ea5u. T\u00f4i c\u1ea7n ph\u1ea3i l\u00e0 m\u1ed9t c\u1ea7u th\u1ee7 quan tr\u1ecdng \u1edf m\u1ed9t CLB v\u00e0 t\u00f4i ngh\u0129 r\u1eb1ng \u0111i\u1ec1u \u0111\u00f3 ch\u1ec9 c\u00f3 th\u1ec3 x\u1ea3y ra v\u1edbi m\u1ed9t b\u1ea3n h\u1ee3p \u0111\u1ed3ng l\u00e2u d\u00e0i.\u201d<br>\r\n<br>\r\n\u201cT\u00f4i c\u00f2n 1 n\u0103m h\u1ee3p \u0111\u1ed3ng v\u1edbi Man City v\u00e0 kh\u00f4ng c\u00f2n mu\u1ed1n thi \u0111\u1ea5u d\u01b0\u1edbi d\u1ea1ng cho m\u01b0\u1ee3n. T\u00ecnh h\u00ecnh \u0111\u00e3 \u0111\u1ed5i kh\u00e1c v\u00e0 t\u00f4i mu\u1ed1n \u0111\u01b0\u1ee3c coi tr\u1ecdng h\u01a1n. Th\u1eadt kh\u00f3 kh\u0103n khi b\u1ea1n b\u1ecb \u0111em cho m\u01b0\u1ee3n, \u0111\u1eb7c bi\u1ec7t khi b\u1ea1n kh\u00f4ng ph\u1ea3i l\u00e0 m\u1ed9t c\u1ea7u th\u1ee7 tr\u1ebb m\u00e0 m\u1ecdi ng\u01b0\u1eddi c\u00f3 th\u1ec3 th\u00f4ng c\u1ea3m.\u201d<br>\r\n<br>\r\n<strong>Xem th\u00eam m\u1ed9t s\u1ed1 b\u00e0i vi\u1ebft v\u1ec1 chuy\u1ec3n nh\u01b0\u1ee3ng Man City tr\u00ean Bongda24h.vn:<br>\r\n<br>\r\n<div class=\"articlerelatepannel\">\r\n<div class=\"articlerelate\"><span href=\"/bong-da-anh/man-city-len-ke-hoach-chia-tay-sterling-172-191666.html\">Man City l\u00ean k\u1ebf ho\u1ea1ch chia tay c\u00f4ng th\u1ea7n tr\u01b0\u1edbc m\u00f9a gi\u1ea3i m\u1edbi</span></div>\r\n<div class=\"articlerelate\"><span href=\"/bong-da-anh/man-city-bo-cuoc-vu-mateo-kovacic-172-191406.html\">\u0110\u1ea1i gia \u0111\u1ea7u ti\u00ean tuy\u00ean b\u1ed1 b\u1ecf cu\u1ed9c v\u1ee5 Mateo Kovacic</span></div>\r\n<div class=\"articlerelate\"><span href=\"/world-cup-2018/vua-sang-man-city-bom-tan-mahrez-da-no-tung-troi-421-191068.html\">V\u1eeba sang Man City, bom t\u1ea5n Mahrez \u0111\u00e3 \u201cn\u1ed5\u201d tung tr\u1eddi</span></div>\r\n<div class=\"articlerelate\"><span href=\"/bong-da-anh/bom-tan-60-trieu-bang-riyad-mahrez-cua-man-city-khung-khiep-co-nao-172-191050.html\">\u201cBom t\u1ea5n\u201d 60 tri\u1ec7u b\u1ea3ng Riyad Mahrez c\u1ee7a Man City kh\u1ee7ng khi\u1ebfp c\u1ee1 n\u00e0o?</span></div>\r\n<div class=\"articlerelate\"><span href=\"/bong-da-anh/man-city-chieu-mo-thanh-cong-mahrez-172-190895.html\">Man City CH\u00cdNH TH\u1ee8C ho\u00e0n t\u1ea5t \u201cbom t\u1ea5n\u201d 60 tri\u1ec7u b\u1ea3ng</span></div>\r\n</div>\r\n<br>\r\n<br>\r\n\u00dd An (TTVN)</strong><br>\r\n\u00a0</div></div><advbottom>","new_url":"","id":"4482","checkdouble":"191782"},{"date":"15:46 22/07","title":"Chelsea nh\u1eafm m\u1ed9t c\u1eb7p th\u1ee7 m\u00f4n tuy\u1ec3n Anh thay Courtois","type":"B\u00f3ng \u0111\u00e1 Anh","img_url":"https://static.bongda24h.vn/medias/thumnail/2018/7/22/2-thu-mon-tuyen-Anh-Butland-Pickford.jpg","new_desc":"<link href='https://bongda24h.vn/websites/css/stylemobilev3.css?v=3' rel='stylesheet' type='text/css' /><style>body{margin:0px; padding:3px; font-size: 20px;}*{font-size:20px !important;}.articlerelatepannel { display:none; padding: 6px;  margin-top:5px; margin-bottom:5px; background-color:#f7f7f7; border:solid 1px #0cac0c}.mediaplayercontent{display:none;}h1{font-size:24px; font-weight:bold; color:black;}h2{font-weight:bold; color:black; width:100%; margin-top:5px !important;}h3{font-weight:bold; color:black;}iframe{display:none;}</style><div class='chitiet_tin'><h2>Chelsea mu\u1ed1n mua Pickford v\u00e0 Butland. H\u1ecd tin r\u1eb1ng nh\u1eefng c\u00e1i t\u00ean n\u00e0y \u0111\u1ee7 s\u1ee9c thay th\u1ebf th\u1ee7 m\u00f4n Courtois r\u1ea5t c\u00f3 th\u1ec3 s\u1ebd gia nh\u1eadp Real Madrid m\u00f9a h\u00e8 n\u00e0y.</h2><div style=\"text-align: justify;\">\u00a0</div>\r\n<h2>Courtois s\u1eafp r\u1eddi Chelsea</h2>\r\n</div><mobileadv><link href='https://bongda24h.vn/websites/css/stylemobilev3.css?v=3' rel='stylesheet' type='text/css' /><style>body{margin:0px; padding:3px; font-size: 20px;}*{font-size:20px !important;}.articlerelatepannel { display:none; padding: 6px;  margin-top:5px; margin-bottom:5px; background-color:#f7f7f7; border:solid 1px #0cac0c}.mediaplayercontent{display:none;}h1{font-size:24px; font-weight:bold; color:black;}h2{font-weight:bold; color:black; width:100%; margin-top:5px !important;}h3{font-weight:bold; color:black;}iframe{display:none;}</style><div class='chitiet_tin'><div style=\"text-align: justify;\"><br>\r\nH\u1ee3p \u0111\u1ed3ng c\u1ee7a Thibaut Courtois v\u1edbi Chelsea ch\u1ec9 c\u00f2n 1 n\u0103m n\u1eefa l\u00e0 \u0111\u00e1o h\u1ea1n. Nh\u1eefng n\u1ed7 l\u1ef1c gia h\u1ea1n h\u1ee3p \u0111\u1ed3ng v\u1edbi th\u1ee7 m\u00f4n 26 tu\u1ed5i c\u1ee7a The Blues \u0111ang \u0111i v\u00e0o ng\u00f5 c\u1ee5t. T\u1eeb l\u00e2u, Courtois \u0111\u00e3 \u0111\u00e1nh ti\u1ebfng mu\u1ed1n tr\u1edf l\u1ea1i Madrid, n\u01a1i hai ng\u01b0\u1eddi con c\u1ee7a anh v\u1eabn sinh s\u1ed1ng.<br>\r\n<br>\r\nSau World Cup 2018, Courtois c\u00e0ng mu\u1ed1n tr\u1edf l\u1ea1i th\u1ee7 \u0111\u00f4 T\u00e2y Ban Nha h\u01a1n. \u1ede \u0111\u00e2y c\u00f3 m\u1ed9t \u0111\u1ea1i gia \u0111ang ch\u00e0o \u0111\u00f3n anh \u0111\u00f3 l\u00e0 Real Madrid. Los Blancos r\u1ea5t ch\u00fa \u00fd t\u1edbi t\u01b0\u01a1ng lai c\u1ee7a th\u1ee7 m\u00f4n ng\u01b0\u1eddi B\u1ec9 v\u00e0 nh\u1eadn th\u1ea5y nh\u1eefng d\u1ea5u hi\u1ec7u t\u00edch c\u1ef1c.<br>\r\n<br>\r\n<div style=\"text-align: center; width: 100%\" class=\"imagecontainer\">\r\n<table style=\"text-align: center; width:100%;\">\r\n    <tbody>\r\n        <tr style=\"width:100%;\">\r\n            <td style=\"width:100%; text-align: center;\" align=\"center\"><img style=\"border: none\" alt=\"Chelsea mu\u1ed1n mua Pickford v\u00e0 Butland thay Courtois h\u00ecnh \u1ea3nh\" title=\"Chelsea mu\u1ed1n mua Pickford v\u00e0 Butland thay Courtois h\u00ecnh \u1ea3nh\" src=\"https://static.bongda24h.vn/medias/mobile/2018/7/3/Chelsea-muon-mua-Pickford-va-Butland-thay-Courtois-hinh-anh.jpg\"></td>\r\n        </tr>\r\n        <tr>\r\n            <td style=\"text-align: center\">Courtois nhi\u1ec1u kh\u1ea3 n\u0103ng r\u1eddi Chelsea</td>\r\n        </tr>\r\n    </tbody>\r\n</table>\r\n</div>\r\n<br>\r\n\u0110i\u1ec1u duy nh\u1ea5t c\u00f3 th\u1ec3 n\u00edu k\u00e9o Courtois \u1edf l\u1ea1i Chelsea l\u00e0 m\u1ee9c \u0111\u00e3i ng\u1ed9 c\u0169ng kh\u00f4ng \u0111\u01b0\u1ee3c \u0111\u00e1p \u1ee9ng. C\u1ee5 th\u1ec3, anh mu\u1ed1n 300 ngh\u00ecn b\u1ea3ng/ tu\u1ea7n trong h\u1ee3p \u0111\u1ed3ng m\u1edbi song CLB ch\u1ee7 qu\u1ea3n ch\u1ec9 \u0111\u00e1p \u1ee9ng \u0111\u01b0\u1ee3c 200 ngh\u00ecn b\u1ea3ng/ tu\u1ea7n.<br>\r\n\u00a0</div>\r\n<h2>The Blues t\u00ecm ng\u01b0\u1eddi thay</h2>\r\n<div style=\"text-align: justify;\"><br>\r\nBan \u0111\u1ea7u, Chelsea nh\u1eafm t\u1edbi Alisson thay Courtois. Nh\u01b0ng sau khi th\u1ee7 th\u00e0nh ng\u01b0\u1eddi Brazil gia nh\u1eadp Liverpool, k\u1ebf ho\u1ea1ch c\u1ee7a h\u1ecd \u0111\u00e3 thay \u0111\u1ed5i. Chelsea mu\u1ed1n mua Pickford v\u00e0 Butland, 2 th\u1ee7 m\u00f4n Anh m\u1edbi tham d\u1ef1 World Cup 2018.<br>\r\n<br>\r\n<div style=\"text-align: center; width: 100%\" class=\"imagecontainer\">\r\n<table style=\"text-align: center; width:100%;\">\r\n    <tbody>\r\n        <tr style=\"width:100%;\">\r\n            <td style=\"width:100%; text-align: center;\" align=\"center\"><img style=\"border: none\" alt=\"2 thu mon tuyen Anh Butland Pickford\" title=\"2 thu mon tuyen Anh Butland Pickford\" src=\"https://static.bongda24h.vn/medias/mobile/2018/7/22/2-thu-mon-tuyen-Anh-Butland-Pickford.jpg\"></td>\r\n        </tr>\r\n        <tr>\r\n            <td style=\"text-align: center\">\r\n            <h3>Chelsea mu\u1ed1n mua Pickford v\u00e0 Butland</h3>\r\n            </td>\r\n        </tr>\r\n    </tbody>\r\n</table>\r\n</div>\r\n<br>\r\nCh\u01b0a khi n\u00e0o Jordan Pickford \u0111\u01b0\u1ee3c \u0111\u00e1nh gi\u00e1 cao nh\u01b0 b\u00e2y gi\u1edd. M\u00e0n tr\u00ecnh di\u1ec5n xu\u1ea5t s\u1eafc c\u1ee7a ng\u01b0\u1eddi g\u00e1c \u0111\u1ec1n 24 tu\u1ed5i t\u1ea1i World Cup 2018 khi\u1ebfn m\u1ee9c gi\u00e1 c\u1ee7a anh t\u0103ng l\u00ean 60 tri\u1ec7u b\u1ea3ng. Hi\u1ec7n ch\u01b0a r\u00f5 Pickford c\u00f3 mu\u1ed1n r\u1eddi Everton ch\u1ec9 sau 1 n\u0103m gia nh\u1eadp hay kh\u00f4ng.<br>\r\n<br>\r\nTuy nhi\u00ean, tr\u01b0\u1eddng h\u1ee3p c\u1ee7a Jack Butland l\u1ea1i thu\u1eadn l\u1ee3i h\u01a1n nhi\u1ec1u. CLB ch\u1ee7 qu\u1ea3n Stoke City c\u1ee7a anh m\u1edbi xu\u1ed1ng h\u1ea1ng v\u00e0 kh\u00f3 l\u00f2ng t\u1eeb ch\u1ed1i c\u01a1 h\u1ed9i t\u1edbi Chelsea. S\u1ed1 ti\u1ec1n 20 tri\u1ec7u b\u1ea3ng l\u00e0 \u0111\u1ee7 \u0111\u1ec3 The Blues c\u00f3 \u0111\u01b0\u1ee3c th\u1ee7 th\u00e0nh 25 tu\u1ed5i.<br>\r\n<br>\r\n<strong>Xem th\u00eam m\u1ed9t s\u1ed1 b\u00e0i vi\u1ebft v\u1ec1 chuy\u1ec3n nh\u01b0\u1ee3ng Chelsea tr\u00ean Bongda24h.vn:<br>\r\n<br>\r\n<div class=\"articlerelatepannel\">\r\n<div class=\"articlerelate\"><span href=\"/bong-da-anh/chelsea-nang-gia-hoi-mua-sao-khung-juventus-len-53-trieu-bang-172-191762.html\">Chelsea n\u00e2ng gi\u00e1 h\u1ecfi mua sao kh\u1ee7ng Juventus l\u00ean 53 tri\u1ec7u b\u1ea3ng</span></div>\r\n<div class=\"articlerelate\"><span href=\"/bong-da-anh/atletico-muon-co-giroud-tu-chelsea-172-191744.html\">L\u1ed9 di\u1ec7n CLB mu\u1ed1n thanh l\u00fd Giroud \u201cgi\u00fap\u201d Chelsea</span></div>\r\n<div class=\"articlerelate\"><span href=\"/bong-da-anh/jeremie-boga-roi-chelsea-toi-sassuolo-172-191736.html\">T\u00e0i n\u0103ng tr\u1ebb Chelsea \u0111\u1ebfn Serie A ch\u01a1i b\u00f3ng</span></div>\r\n<div class=\"articlerelate\"><span href=\"/bong-da-anh/100-golovin-cap-ben-chelsea-o-he-2018-172-191734.html\">100% Golovin c\u1eadp b\u1ebfn Chelsea \u1edf H\u00e8 2018</span></div>\r\n<div class=\"articlerelate\"><span href=\"/bong-da-anh/chelsea-bi-mat-dam-phan-mua-higuain-172-191728.html\">Chelsea b\u00ed m\u1eadt \u0111\u00e0m ph\u00e1n mua ti\u1ec1n \u0111\u1ea1o m\u1edbi thay Morata</span></div>\r\n</div>\r\n<br>\r\n<br>\r\nGia Vi (TTVN)<br>\r\n</strong></div></div><advbottom>","new_url":"","id":"4481","checkdouble":"191787"},{"date":"16:25 22/07","title":"\u0110\u00e2y! 2 c\u00e1i t\u00ean Chelsea nh\u1eafm thay Hazard","type":"B\u00f3ng \u0111\u00e1 Anh","img_url":"https://static.bongda24h.vn/medias/original/2017/10/12/chelsea-muon-mua-isco-va-asensio.jpg","new_desc":"<link href='https://bongda24h.vn/websites/css/stylemobilev3.css?v=3' rel='stylesheet' type='text/css' /><style>body{margin:0px; padding:3px; font-size: 20px;}*{font-size:20px !important;}.articlerelatepannel { display:none; padding: 6px;  margin-top:5px; margin-bottom:5px; background-color:#f7f7f7; border:solid 1px #0cac0c}.mediaplayercontent{display:none;}h1{font-size:24px; font-weight:bold; color:black;}h2{font-weight:bold; color:black; width:100%; margin-top:5px !important;}h3{font-weight:bold; color:black;}iframe{display:none;}</style><div class='chitiet_tin'><h2>Chelsea mu\u1ed1n mua Isco v\u00e0 Asensio. \u0110\u1ed9i b\u00f3ng Anh \u0111ang r\u1ea5t c\u1ea7n nh\u00e2n t\u00e0i thay th\u1ebf Eden Hazard n\u1ebfu anh chuy\u1ec3n t\u1edbi Real Madrid trong m\u00f9a h\u00e8 n\u00e0y.</h2><div style=\"text-align: justify;\">\u00a0</div>\r\n<h2>Hazard mu\u1ed1n r\u1eddi Chelsea</h2>\r\n</div><mobileadv><link href='https://bongda24h.vn/websites/css/stylemobilev3.css?v=3' rel='stylesheet' type='text/css' /><style>body{margin:0px; padding:3px; font-size: 20px;}*{font-size:20px !important;}.articlerelatepannel { display:none; padding: 6px;  margin-top:5px; margin-bottom:5px; background-color:#f7f7f7; border:solid 1px #0cac0c}.mediaplayercontent{display:none;}h1{font-size:24px; font-weight:bold; color:black;}h2{font-weight:bold; color:black; width:100%; margin-top:5px !important;}h3{font-weight:bold; color:black;}iframe{display:none;}</style><div class='chitiet_tin'><div style=\"text-align: justify;\"><br>\r\nSau World Cup 2018, Eden Hazard kh\u00f4ng gi\u1ea5u \u00fd \u0111\u1ecbnh r\u1eddi Chelsea. Tuy\u1ec3n th\u1ee7 B\u1ec9 t\u00e2m s\u1ef1 r\u1eb1ng sau 6 n\u0103m g\u1eafn b\u00f3, \u0111\u00e3 t\u1edbi l\u00fac anh t\u00ecm ki\u1ebfm s\u1ef1 kh\u00e1c bi\u1ec7t trong s\u1ef1 nghi\u1ec7p. Hazard \u0111ang ch\u1edd \u0111\u1ee3i s\u1ef1 cho ph\u00e9p c\u1ee7a CLB ch\u1ee7 qu\u1ea3n \u0111\u1ec3 t\u1edbi v\u1edbi b\u1ebfn \u0111\u1ed7 mong mu\u1ed1n.<br>\r\n<br>\r\nKh\u00f4ng n\u00f3i ra, ai c\u0169ng hi\u1ec3u Hazard mu\u1ed1n t\u1edbi Real Madrid. \u0110\u1ed9i b\u00f3ng T\u00e2y Ban Nha \u0111ang r\u1ea5t c\u1ea7n m\u1ed9t ng\u00f4i sao l\u1edbn thay th\u1ebf Cristiano Ronaldo m\u1edbi d\u1ee9t \u00e1o sang Juventus v\u1edbi gi\u00e1 112 tri\u1ec7u Euro.<br>\r\n<br>\r\n<div style=\"text-align: center; width: 100%\" class=\"imagecontainer\">\r\n<table style=\"text-align: center; width:100%;\">\r\n    <tbody>\r\n        <tr style=\"width:100%;\">\r\n            <td style=\"width:100%; text-align: center;\" align=\"center\"><img style=\"border: none\" alt=\"Chelsea mu\u1ed1n mua Isco v\u00e0 Asensio thay th\u1ebf Hazard h\u00ecnh \u1ea3nh\" title=\"Chelsea mu\u1ed1n mua Isco v\u00e0 Asensio thay th\u1ebf Hazard h\u00ecnh \u1ea3nh\" src=\"https://static.bongda24h.vn/medias/mobile/2018/7/17/Chelsea-muon-mua-Isco-va-Asensio-thay-the-Hazard-hinh-anh.jpg\"></td>\r\n        </tr>\r\n        <tr>\r\n            <td style=\"text-align: center\">Real r\u1ea5t mu\u1ed1n c\u00f3 Hazard thay Ronaldo</td>\r\n        </tr>\r\n    </tbody>\r\n</table>\r\n</div>\r\n<br>\r\nTheo th\u00f4ng tin m\u00e0 t\u1edd Le10 Sport c\u00f3 \u0111\u01b0\u1ee3c, Real s\u1eb5n s\u00e0ng chi s\u1ed1 ti\u1ec1n 170 tri\u1ec7u b\u1ea3ng \u0111\u1ec3 ho\u00e0n t\u1ea5t h\u1ee3p \u0111\u1ed3ng v\u1edbi Hazard. H\u1ee3p \u0111\u1ed3ng c\u1ee7a c\u1ea7u th\u1ee7 27 tu\u1ed5i v\u1edbi Chelsea ch\u1ec9 c\u00f2n 2 n\u0103m v\u00e0 kh\u00f4ng c\u00f3 \u00fd \u0111\u1ecbnh k\u00e9o d\u00e0i.<br>\r\n\u00a0</div>\r\n<h2>The Blues nh\u1eafm Isco v\u00e0 Asensio</h2>\r\n<div style=\"text-align: justify;\"><br>\r\nChelsea mu\u1ed1n mua Isco v\u00e0 Asensio c\u1ee7a Real. T\u00e2n HLV Maurizio Sarri c\u1ee7a h\u1ecd nh\u1eafm c\u1eb7p \u0111\u00f4i n\u00e0y thay th\u1ebf Eden Hazard trong tr\u01b0\u1eddng h\u1ee3p anh quy\u1ebft ra \u0111i. Tr\u01b0\u1edbc \u0111\u00e2y, Real t\u1eebng nh\u1eafm t\u1edbi Harry Kane, Mo Salah song h\u1ecd \u0111\u1ec1u \u0111\u00e3 gia h\u1ea1n h\u1ee3p \u0111\u1ed3ng v\u1edbi Tottenham v\u00e0 Liverpool.<br>\r\n<br>\r\n<div style=\"text-align: center; width: 100%\" class=\"imagecontainer\">\r\n<table style=\"text-align: center; width:100%;\">\r\n    <tbody>\r\n        <tr style=\"width:100%;\">\r\n            <td style=\"width:100%; text-align: center;\" align=\"center\"><img style=\"border: none\" alt=\"Isco va Asensio tai Real\" title=\"Isco va Asensio tai Real\" src=\"https://static.bongda24h.vn/medias/mobile/2017/10/12/chelsea-muon-mua-isco-va-asensio.jpg\"></td>\r\n        </tr>\r\n        <tr>\r\n            <td style=\"text-align: center\">\r\n            <h3>Chelsea mu\u1ed1n mua Isco v\u00e0 Asensio</h3>\r\n            </td>\r\n        </tr>\r\n    </tbody>\r\n</table>\r\n</div>\r\n<br>\r\nLos Blancos m\u1edbi nh\u1eafm t\u1edbi Kylian Mbappe v\u00e0 Neymar c\u1ee7a PSG song g\u1eb7p ph\u1ea3i s\u1ef1 ng\u0103n c\u1ea3n t\u1edbi t\u1eeb \u0111\u1ea1i gia n\u01b0\u1edbc Ph\u00e1p. \u0110i\u1ec1u \u0111\u00f3 c\u00e0ng khi\u1ebfn l\u00e3nh \u0111\u1ea1o Real mu\u1ed1n s\u1edf h\u1eefu Hazard nhi\u1ec1u h\u01a1n.<br>\r\n<br>\r\nTuy nhi\u00ean, Chelsea tuy\u00ean b\u1ed1 s\u1ebd ch\u1ec9 b\u00e1n Hazard n\u1ebfu t\u00ecm \u0111\u01b0\u1ee3c ng\u01b0\u1eddi thay th\u1ebf. Ch\u1eb3ng ki\u1ebfm \u0111\u00e2u xa, The Blues mu\u1ed1n trao \u0111\u1ed5i ng\u01b0\u1eddi v\u1edbi \u0111\u1ed1i t\u00e1c Real. Trong kho\u1ea3ng 2 n\u0103m tr\u1edf l\u1ea1i \u0111\u00e2y, Isco v\u00e0 Asensio \u0111\u00e3 tr\u01b0\u1edfng th\u00e0nh kh\u00f4ng \u00edt t\u1ea1i s\u00e2n Santiago Bernabeu.<br>\r\n<br>\r\nD\u00f9 v\u1eady, khi \u0111ang kh\u00e1t sao t\u1ea7m c\u1ee1 th\u1ebf gi\u1edbi nh\u01b0 Hazard, ch\u01b0a bi\u1ebft ch\u1eebng Real s\u1ebd \u0111\u1ed3ng \u00fd nh\u1ea3 Isco v\u00e0 Asensio. Nh\u1eefng Karrim Benzema v\u00e0 Gareth Bale nhi\u1ec1u kh\u1ea3 n\u0103ng kh\u00f4ng r\u1eddi \u0111i v\u00e0 khi \u0111\u00f3 v\u1ecb tr\u00ed c\u1ee7a b\u1ed9 \u0111\u00f4i ng\u01b0\u1eddi T\u00e2y Ban Nha c\u00f3 th\u1ec3 s\u1ebd l\u00e0 tr\u00ean gh\u1ebf d\u1ef1 b\u1ecb.<br>\r\n<strong><br>\r\nXem th\u00eam m\u1ed9t s\u1ed1 b\u00e0i vi\u1ebft v\u1ec1 chuy\u1ec3n nh\u01b0\u1ee3ng Chelsea tr\u00ean Bongda24h.vn:<br>\r\n<br>\r\n<div class=\"articlerelatepannel\">\r\n<div class=\"articlerelate\"><span href=\"/bong-da-anh/chelsea-muon-mua-pickford-va-butland-172-191787.html\">Chelsea nh\u1eafm m\u1ed9t c\u1eb7p th\u1ee7 m\u00f4n tuy\u1ec3n Anh thay Courtois</span></div>\r\n<div class=\"articlerelate\"><span href=\"/bong-da-anh/tan-hlv-chelsea-bi-chi-trich-te-bac-voi-doi-bong-cu-napoli-172-191768.html\">T\u00e2n HLV Chelsea b\u1ecb ch\u1ec9 tr\u00edch ph\u1ee5 b\u1ea1c v\u1edbi \u0111\u1ed9i b\u00f3ng c\u0169 Napoli</span></div>\r\n<div class=\"articlerelate\"><span href=\"/bong-da-anh/chelsea-nang-gia-hoi-mua-sao-khung-juventus-len-53-trieu-bang-172-191762.html\">Chelsea n\u00e2ng gi\u00e1 h\u1ecfi mua sao kh\u1ee7ng Juventus l\u00ean 53 tri\u1ec7u b\u1ea3ng</span></div>\r\n<div class=\"articlerelate\"><span href=\"/bong-da-anh/atletico-muon-co-giroud-tu-chelsea-172-191744.html\">L\u1ed9 di\u1ec7n CLB mu\u1ed1n thanh l\u00fd Giroud \u201cgi\u00fap\u201d Chelsea</span></div>\r\n<div class=\"articlerelate\"><span href=\"/bong-da-anh/jeremie-boga-roi-chelsea-toi-sassuolo-172-191736.html\">T\u00e0i n\u0103ng tr\u1ebb Chelsea \u0111\u1ebfn Serie A ch\u01a1i b\u00f3ng</span></div>\r\n</div>\r\n<br>\r\n<br>\r\nGia Vi (TTVN)<br>\r\n</strong></div></div><advbottom>","new_url":"","id":"4480","checkdouble":"191788"},{"date":"11:16 22/07","title":"Nh\u1eadn \u0111\u1ecbnh Liverpool vs Dortmund 03h00 ng\u00e0y 23/7 (ICC 2018)","type":"B\u00f3ng \u0111\u00e1 Ch\u00e2u \u00c2u","img_url":"https://static.bongda24h.vn/medias/original/2018/7/22/nhan-dinh-liverpool-vs-dortmund-03h00-ngay-237-icc-2018.jpg","new_desc":"<link href='https://bongda24h.vn/websites/css/stylemobilev3.css?v=3' rel='stylesheet' type='text/css' /><style>body{margin:0px; padding:3px; font-size: 20px;}*{font-size:20px !important;}.articlerelatepannel { display:none; padding: 6px;  margin-top:5px; margin-bottom:5px; background-color:#f7f7f7; border:solid 1px #0cac0c}.mediaplayercontent{display:none;}h1{font-size:24px; font-weight:bold; color:black;}h2{font-weight:bold; color:black; width:100%; margin-top:5px !important;}h3{font-weight:bold; color:black;}iframe{display:none;}</style><div class='chitiet_tin'><h2>Liverpool vs Dortmund l\u00fac 03h00 ng\u00e0y 23/7 (Gi\u1ea3i giao h\u1eefu International Champions Cup ICC 2018): Nh\u1eadn \u0111\u1ecbnh b\u00f3ng \u0111\u00e1, \u00fd ki\u1ebfn chuy\u00ean gia, d\u1ef1 \u0111o\u00e1n k\u1ebft qu\u1ea3, ph\u00e2n t\u00edch chuy\u00ean m\u00f4n, c\u00e1c th\u00f4ng tin, th\u1ed1ng k\u00ea b\u00ean l\u1ec1 tr\u01b0\u1edbc tr\u1eadn \u0111\u1ea5u.</h2><div style=\"text-align: center; width: 100%\" class=\"imagecontainer\">\r\n<table style=\"text-align: center; width:100%;\">\r\n    <tbody>\r\n        <tr style=\"width:100%;\">\r\n            <td style=\"width:100%; text-align: center;\" align=\"center\"><img style=\"border: none\" alt=\"Nh\u1eadn \u0111\u1ecbnh Liverpool vs Dortmund 03h00 ng\u00e0y 237 ICC 2018 h\u00ecnh \u1ea3nh\" title=\"Nh\u1eadn \u0111\u1ecbnh Liverpool vs Dortmund 03h00 ng\u00e0y 237 ICC 2018 h\u00ecnh \u1ea3nh\" src=\"https://static.bongda24h.vn/medias/mobile/2018/7/22/lich-thi-dau-bong-da-hom-nay-2272018.jpg\"></td>\r\n        </tr>\r\n        <tr>\r\n            <td style=\"text-align: center\">Liverpool vs Dortmund</td>\r\n        </tr>\r\n    </tbody>\r\n</table>\r\n</div>\r\n<br>\r\n<h2 style=\"color: rgb(0, 0, 0); font-family: Arial, Verdana, sans-serif; font-style: normal; font-variant-ligatures: normal; font-variant-caps: normal; letter-spacing: normal; text-indent: 0px; text-transform: none; white-space: normal; word-spacing: 0px; -webkit-text-stroke-width: 0px; background-color: rgb(255, 255, 255); text-decoration-style: initial; text-decoration-color: initial;\"><span href=\"https://bongda24h.vn/nhan-dinh-bong-da-c344-p1.html\" target=\"_blank\">Nh\u1eadn \u0111\u1ecbnh b\u00f3ng \u0111\u00e1</span><span><span><span><span><span><span><span><span><span><span><span><span><span><span><span><span><span><span><span><span><span><span><span><span><span><span><span><span><span><span><span><span><span><span><span><span><span><span><span><span><span><span><span><span><span><span><span><span> </span></span></span></span></span></span></span></span>Liverpool vs Dortmund: 3-1</span></span></span></span></span></span></span></span></span></span></span></span></span></span></span></span></span></span></span></span></span></span></span></span></span></span></span></span></span></span></span></span></span></span></span></span></span></span></span></span></h2>\r\n<div>M\u1eb7c d\u00f9 c\u00f2n h\u01a1n 1 th\u00e1ng n\u1eefa TTCN m\u00f9a H\u00e8 m\u1edbi kh\u00e9p l\u1ea1i nh\u01b0ng c\u00f3 th\u1ec3 n\u00f3i Liverpool \u0111\u00e3 g\u1ea7n nh\u01b0 ho\u00e0n t\u1ea5t ho\u1ea1t \u0111\u1ed9ng chuy\u1ec3n nh\u01b0\u1ee3ng. R\u1ea5t nhanh, The Kop \u0111\u00e3 mang v\u1ec1 \u0111\u01b0\u1ee3c nh\u1eefng t\u00e2n binh r\u1ea5t ch\u1ea5t l\u01b0\u1ee3ng nh\u01b0 Fabinho, Shaqiri hay m\u1edbi nh\u1ea5t l\u00e0 th\u1ee7 th\u00e0nh Alisson. Ch\u01b0a h\u1ebft, ngay t\u1eeb n\u0103m ngo\u00e1i th\u00ec Liverpool c\u0169ng chi\u00eau m\u1ed9 xong ti\u1ec1n v\u1ec7 trung t\u00e2m Naby Keita. Ngh\u0129a l\u00e0, t\u1edbi th\u1eddi \u0111i\u1ec3m n\u00e0y The Kop \u0111\u00e3 c\u00f3 4 s\u1ef1 t\u0103ng c\u01b0\u1eddng \u1edf \u0111\u1ec1u 3 tuy\u1ebfn. V\u00e0 \u0111\u00f3 \u0111\u1ec1u l\u00e0 nh\u1eefng t\u00e2n binh \u0111\u01b0\u1ee3c \u0111\u00e1nh gi\u00e1 r\u1ea5t cao, h\u1ee9a h\u1eb9n s\u1ebd t\u0103ng c\u01b0\u1eddng th\u00eam r\u1ea5t nhi\u1ec1u s\u1ee9c m\u1ea1nh cho \u0111\u1ed9i qu\u00e2n c\u1ee7a HLV Juergen Klopp. <br>\r\n<br>\r\nVi\u1ec7c Liverpool shopping r\u1ea5t nhanh v\u00e0 m\u1ea1nh tay \u1edf phi\u00ean ch\u1ee3 m\u00f9a H\u00e8 c\u0169ng cho th\u1ea5y tham v\u1ecdng v\u00e0 k\u1ef3 v\u1ecdng r\u1ea5t l\u1edbn c\u1ee7a h\u1ecd \u1edf m\u00f9a gi\u1ea3i s\u1eafp t\u1edbi. M\u00f9a b\u00f3ng tr\u01b0\u1edbc, h\u1ecd \u0111\u00e3 v\u00e0o t\u1edbi tr\u1eadn chung k\u1ebft Champions League. \u1ede Premier League th\u00ec The Kop lu\u00f4n \u1ed5n \u0111\u1ecbnh \u1edf v\u1ecb tr\u00ed trong Top 4. N\u0103m nay, Klopp ch\u1eafc ch\u1eafn h\u01b0\u1edbng t\u1edbi m\u1ee5c ti\u00eau xa h\u01a1n l\u00e0 c\u1ea1nh tranh s\u00f2ng ph\u1eb3ng ch\u1ee9c v\u00f4 \u0111\u1ecbch Premier League v\u1edbi Man City. V\u00e0 v\u1edbi nh\u1eefng t\u00e2n binh h\u00e0ng hi\u1ec7u k\u1ec3 tr\u00ean, c\u1ed9ng v\u1edbi d\u00e0n ng\u00f4i sao s\u1eb5n c\u00f3 nh\u01b0 Mohamed Salah, Roberto Firmino, Sadio Mane, Van Dijk, Jordan Henderson\u2026, c\u00f3 th\u1ec3 n\u00f3i Liverpool \u0111ang r\u1ea5t t\u1ef1 tin tr\u01b0\u1edbc gi\u1edd Premier League 2018/19 kh\u1edfi tranh. <br>\r\n<br>\r\nS\u1ef1 t\u1ef1 tin v\u00e0 quy\u1ebft t\u00e2m c\u0169ng l\u00e0 \u0111i\u1ec1u The Kop \u0111ang th\u1ec3 hi\u1ec7n \u0111\u01b0\u1ee3c \u1edf lo\u1ea1t tr\u1eadn giao h\u1eefu m\u00f9a H\u00e8. H\u1ecd l\u00e0 \u0111\u1ed9i h\u1ed9i qu\u00e2n v\u00e0 \u0111\u00e1 giao h\u1eefu s\u1edbm nh\u1ea5t trong Big Six. Ngay t\u1eeb nh\u1eefng ng\u00e0y \u0111\u1ea7u th\u00e1ng 7, Liverpool \u0111\u00e3 ch\u01a1i tr\u1eadn \u0111\u1ea7u ti\u00ean c\u1ee7a m\u00f9a H\u00e8. \u0110\u1ebfn th\u1eddi \u0111i\u1ec3m n\u00e0y, The Kop \u0111\u00e3 th\u1eafng 3 v\u00e0 ch\u1ec9 ho\u00e0 1/4 tr\u1eadn giao h\u1eefu. M\u1edbi nh\u1ea5t l\u00e0 chi\u1ebfn th\u1eafng 2-0 tr\u01b0\u1edbc \u0111\u1ed1i th\u1ee7 \u0111ang \u0111\u00e1 \u1edf gi\u1ea3i h\u1ea1ng Nh\u1ea5t, Blackburn. Vi\u1ec7c 2 c\u1ea7u th\u1ee7 v\u00e0o s\u00e2n t\u1eeb gh\u1ebf d\u1ef1 b\u1ecb l\u00e0 Daniel Sturridge v\u00e0 Lazar Markovic ghi b\u00e0n mang v\u1ec1 chi\u1ebfn th\u1eafng cho Liverpool c\u0169ng cho th\u1ea5y s\u1ee9c m\u1ea1nh chi\u1ec1u s\u00e2u c\u1ee7a \u0111\u1ed9i b\u00f3ng n\u00e0y. <br>\r\n<br>\r\nHai t\u00e2n binh r\u1ea5t \u0111\u01b0\u1ee3c k\u1ef3 v\u1ecdng l\u00e0 Naby Keita v\u00e0 Fabinho ch\u1ec9 ng\u1ed3i d\u1ef1 b\u1ecb \u1edf tr\u1eadn g\u1eb7p Blackburn. Tuy nhi\u00ean \u0111\u00eam nay th\u00ec nhi\u1ec1u kh\u1ea3 n\u0103ng c\u1eb7p \u0111\u00f4i ti\u1ec1n v\u1ec7 trung t\u00e2m n\u00e0y s\u1ebd \u0111\u00e1 ch\u00ednh. V\u1edbi \u0111\u1ed9i h\u00ecnh ch\u1ea5t l\u01b0\u1ee3ng, l\u1ea1i c\u00f3 s\u1ef1 quy\u1ebft t\u00e2m l\u1edbn, Liverpool nhi\u1ec1u kh\u1ea3 n\u0103ng s\u1ebd l\u00e0 \u0111\u1ed1i th\u1ee7 qu\u00e1 m\u1ea1nh so v\u1edbi Dortmund. B\u1edfi c\u1ea7n bi\u1ebft l\u00e0 \u0111\u1ed9i b\u00f3ng n\u01b0\u1edbc \u0110\u1ee9c m\u1edbi \u0111ang trong nh\u1eefng ng\u00e0y \u0111\u1ea7u d\u01b0\u1edbi s\u1ef1 d\u1eabn d\u1eaft c\u1ee7a t\u00e2n HLV Lucien Favre. C\u1ef1u HLV Nice c\u1ea7n th\u00eam th\u1eddi gian \u0111\u1ec3 hi\u1ec3u c\u00e1c h\u1ecdc tr\u00f2, c\u0169ng nh\u01b0 gi\u00fap c\u00e1c c\u1ea7u th\u1ee7 Dortmund hi\u1ec3u tri\u1ebft l\u00fd ch\u01a1i b\u00f3ng c\u1ee7a m\u00ecnh. <br>\r\n<br>\r\nN\u1ebfu Klopp coi nh\u1eefng tr\u1eadn giao h\u1eefu l\u00e0 c\u01a1 h\u1ed9i \u0111\u1ec3 ho\u00e0n thi\u1ec7n b\u1ed9 khung r\u1ea5t \u1ed5n m\u00e0 \u00f4ng \u0111\u00e3 t\u1ea1o ra th\u00ec Favre l\u1ea1i coi giao h\u1eefu l\u00e0 d\u1ecbp \u0111\u1ec3 \u00f4ng hi\u1ec3u k\u1ef9 h\u01a1n v\u1ec1 t\u1eebng c\u1ea7u th\u1ee7 v\u00e0 th\u1eed nghi\u1ec7m \u0111\u1ed9i h\u00ecnh. C\u0169ng c\u1ea7n bi\u1ebft l\u00e0 trong 4 tr\u1eadn giao h\u1eefu g\u1ea7n nh\u1ea5t, Dortmund \u0111\u00e3 \u0111\u1ec3 2 \u0111\u1ed1i th\u1ee7 y\u1ebfu h\u01a1n r\u1ea5t nhi\u1ec1u c\u1ea7m h\u00f2a. Chi\u1ebfn th\u1eafng 1-0 tr\u01b0\u1edbc Man City m\u1edbi \u0111\u00e2y kh\u00f4ng n\u00f3i l\u00ean nhi\u1ec1u \u0111i\u1ec1u b\u1edfi Pep Guardiola s\u1eed d\u1ee5ng \u0111\u1ed9i h\u00ecnh h\u1ea7u h\u1ebft l\u00e0 c\u1ea7u th\u1ee7 tr\u1ebb. \u1ede nh\u1eefng tr\u1eadn giao h\u1eefu, th\u00e1i \u0111\u1ed9 ti\u1ebfp c\u1eadn tr\u1eadn \u0111\u1ea5u nhi\u1ec1u khi m\u1edbi l\u00e0 y\u1ebfu t\u1ed1 quan tr\u1ecdng nh\u1ea5t quy\u1ebft \u0111\u1ecbnh th\u00e0nh b\u1ea1i. M\u1ed9t Liverpool nghi\u00eam t\u00fac h\u01a1n, l\u1ef1c l\u01b0\u1ee3ng m\u1ea1nh h\u01a1n nhi\u1ec1u kh\u1ea3 n\u0103ng s\u1ebd gi\u00e0nh chi\u1ebfn th\u1eafng. <br>\r\n<br>\r\n\u0110\u00eam nay, Juergen Klopp s\u1ebd l\u1ea1i c\u00f3 d\u1ecbp g\u1eb7p l\u1ea1i \u0111\u1ed9i b\u00f3ng c\u0169 Dortmund. Tr\u01b0\u1edbc khi t\u1edbi Liverpool th\u00ec Klopp t\u1eebng c\u00f3 7 n\u0103m d\u1eabn d\u1eaft Dortmund. Nhi\u1ec1u c\u1ea7u th\u1ee7 c\u1ee7a Dortmund hi\u1ec7n t\u1ea1i t\u1eebng l\u00e0 h\u1ecdc tr\u00f2 c\u0169 c\u1ee7a Klopp, v\u00ed d\u1ee5 nh\u01b0 Mario Goetze. \u0110\u00e1ng ch\u00fa \u00fd, \u0111\u00e2y l\u00e0 l\u1ea7n th\u1ee9 3 Klopp s\u1ebd \u0111\u1ed1i \u0111\u1ea7u Dortmund tr\u00ean c\u01b0\u01a1ng v\u1ecb HLV Liverpool. Hai l\u1ea7n tr\u01b0\u1edbc \u0111\u00f3 l\u00e0 \u1edf v\u00f2ng knock-out Europa League 2015/16. Klopp gi\u00e0nh 1 tr\u1eadn ho\u00e0 v\u00e0 1 tr\u1eadn th\u1eafng. <br>\r\n<br>\r\nHLV Juergen Klopp (Liverpool): \u201cCh\u00fang t\u00f4i kh\u00f4ng mu\u1ed1n b\u1ecf l\u1ee1 b\u1ea5t k\u1ef3 gi\u00e2y ph\u00fat n\u00e0o \u0111\u1ec3 chu\u1ea9n b\u1ecb cho m\u00f9a gi\u1ea3i m\u1edbi. T\u00f4i mu\u1ed1n Liverpool ph\u1ea3i lu\u00f4n s\u1eb5n s\u00e0ng v\u00e0 \u0111\u1eb7t quy\u1ebft t\u00e2m chi\u1ebfn th\u1eafng \u1edf m\u1ecdi tr\u1eadn \u0111\u1ea5u\u201d. <br>\r\n<br>\r\nHLV Lucien Favre (Dortmund): \u201cLiverpool l\u00e0 \u0111\u1ed1i th\u1ee7 r\u1ea5t m\u1ea1nh. H\u1ecd \u0111\u00e3 v\u00e0o t\u1edbi tr\u1eadn chung k\u1ebft Champions League m\u00f9a tr\u01b0\u1edbc. \u0110\u00e2y l\u00e0 tr\u1eadn \u0111\u1ea5u r\u1ea5t b\u1ed5 \u00edch \u0111\u1ec3 c\u00e1c c\u1ea7u th\u1ee7 tr\u1ebb c\u1ee7a t\u00f4i t\u00edch lu\u1ef9 th\u00eam kinh nghi\u1ec7m\u201d. <br>\r\n<br>\r\nTH\u00d4NG TIN<br>\r\n- Liverpool th\u1eafng 8, thua 11/20 tr\u1eadn g\u1ea7n nh\u1ea5t theo ch\u00e2u \u00c1. <br>\r\n- 13/20 tr\u1eadn g\u1ea7n nh\u1ea5t c\u1ee7a Liverpool c\u00f3 t\u1ed1i thi\u1ec3u 3 l\u1ea7n l\u01b0\u1edbi rung. <br>\r\n- Dortmund th\u1eafng 9, thua 11/20 tr\u1eadn g\u1ea7n nh\u1ea5t theo ch\u00e2u \u00c1. <br>\r\n- 9/20 tr\u1eadn g\u1ea7n nh\u1ea5t c\u1ee7a Dortmund c\u00f3 t\u1ed1i thi\u1ec3u 3 b\u00e0n th\u1eafng. <br>\r\n<br>\r\n\u0110\u1eb6C BI\u1ec6T<br>\r\nT\u1ed1i thi\u1ec3u 1 b\u00e0n hi\u1ec7p 1: 15/20 tr\u1eadn g\u1ea7n nh\u1ea5t c\u1ee7a Dortmund c\u00f3 t\u1ed1i thi\u1ec3u 1 l\u1ea7n l\u01b0\u1edbi rung hi\u1ec7p 1. 14/20 tr\u1eadn g\u1ea7n nh\u1ea5t c\u1ee7a Liverpool c\u00f3 k\u1ecbch b\u1ea3n t\u01b0\u01a1ng t\u1ef1. NHM n\u00ean \u0111\u1ee3i sau 15 ph\u00fat \u0111\u1ea7u r\u1ed3i \u0111\u1eb7t ni\u1ec1m tin v\u00e0o t\u1ef7 l\u1ec7 nhi\u1ec1u b\u00e0n hi\u1ec7p 1.</div>\r\n<br>\r\nTheo Bongdaplus.vn<br></div><advbottom>","new_url":"","id":"4479","checkdouble":"191776"},{"date":"09:16 22/07","title":"T\u00e2n HLV Chelsea b\u1ecb ch\u1ec9 tr\u00edch ph\u1ee5 b\u1ea1c v\u1edbi \u0111\u1ed9i b\u00f3ng c\u0169 Napoli","type":"B\u00f3ng \u0111\u00e1 Anh","img_url":"https://static.bongda24h.vn/medias/thumnail/2018/7/14/tan-hlv-chelsea-bi-chi-trich-te-bac-voi-doi-bong-cu-napoli.PNG","new_desc":"<link href='https://bongda24h.vn/websites/css/stylemobilev3.css?v=3' rel='stylesheet' type='text/css' /><style>body{margin:0px; padding:3px; font-size: 20px;}*{font-size:20px !important;}.articlerelatepannel { display:none; padding: 6px;  margin-top:5px; margin-bottom:5px; background-color:#f7f7f7; border:solid 1px #0cac0c}.mediaplayercontent{display:none;}h1{font-size:24px; font-weight:bold; color:black;}h2{font-weight:bold; color:black; width:100%; margin-top:5px !important;}h3{font-weight:bold; color:black;}iframe{display:none;}</style><div class='chitiet_tin'><h2>Ch\u1ee7 t\u1ecbch Aurelio De Laurentiis t\u1ed1 c\u00e1o c\u1ef1u HLV Maurizio Sarri ch\u1ec9 bi\u1ebft r\u00fat ru\u1ed9t \u0111\u1ed9i b\u00f3ng c\u0169 Napoli sau khi ra \u0111i c\u1eadp b\u1ebfn Chelsea.</h2><p class=\"MsoNormal\" style=\"text-align:justify\">M\u00f9a h\u00e8 n\u00e0y, Napoli \u0111\u00e3 b\u1ea5t \u0111\u1eafc d\u0129 \u201cc\u1ed1ng n\u1ea1p\u201d cho Chelsea nh\u1eefng g\u00ec t\u1ed1t nh\u1ea5t c\u1ee7a m\u00ecnh, t\u1eeb HLV Maurizio Sarri \u0111\u1ebfn ti\u1ec1n v\u1ec7 tr\u1ee5 c\u1ed9t Jorginho. \u0110i\u1ec1u n\u00e0y d\u1ec5 d\u00e0ng gi\u1ea3i th\u00edch cho s\u1ef1 cay c\u00fa c\u1ee7a ch\u1ee7 t\u1ecbch Aurelio De Laurentiis \u0111\u1ed1i v\u1edbi ng\u01b0\u1eddi c\u0169 c\u1ee7a m\u00ecnh.</p>\r\n<p class=\"MsoNormal\" style=\"text-align:justify\"><o:p></o:p></p>\r\n<div style=\"text-align: center; width: 100%\" class=\"imagecontainer\">\r\n<table style=\"text-align: center; width:100%;\">\r\n    <tbody>\r\n        <tr style=\"width:100%;\">\r\n            <td style=\"width: 100%;\" align=\"center\"><img style=\"border: none\" alt=\"Ch\u1ee7 t\u1ecbch Napoli ch\u1ec9 tr\u00edch HLV Sarri ph\u1ee5 b\u1ea1c v\u1edbi \u0111\u1ed9i b\u00f3ng c\u0169 h\u00ecnh \u1ea3nh\" title=\"Ch\u1ee7 t\u1ecbch Napoli ch\u1ec9 tr\u00edch HLV Sarri ph\u1ee5 b\u1ea1c v\u1edbi \u0111\u1ed9i b\u00f3ng c\u0169 h\u00ecnh \u1ea3nh\" src=\"https://static.bongda24h.vn/medias/mobile/2018/7/19/Chu-tich-Napoli-chi-trich-HLV-Sarri-phu-bac-voi-doi-bong-cu-hinh-anh.jpg\"></td>\r\n        </tr>\r\n        <tr>\r\n            <td>\r\n            <h3>Ch\u1ee7 t\u1ecbch Napoli ch\u1ec9 tr\u00edch HLV Sarri ph\u1ee5 b\u1ea1c v\u1edbi \u0111\u1ed9i b\u00f3ng c\u0169</h3>\r\n            </td>\r\n        </tr>\r\n    </tbody>\r\n</table>\r\n</div>\r\n<p class=\"MsoNormal\" style=\"text-align:justify\">Th\u1ef1c t\u1ebf tr\u01b0\u1edbc khi quay l\u1ea1i r\u00fat ru\u1ed9t \u0111\u1ed9i b\u00f3ng c\u0169, Sarri v\u00e0 Napoli v\u1ed1n \u0111\u00e3 kh\u00f4ng c\u00f3 m\u00e0n chia tay trong \u00eam \u0111\u1eb9p. Gi\u1edd \u0111\u00e2y, \u00f4ng c\u00f2n b\u1ecb s\u1ebfp c\u0169 l\u00ean \u00e1n s\u1ef1 t\u1ec7 b\u1ea1c, vong \u01a1n b\u1ed9i ngh\u0129a c\u1ee7a m\u00ecnh: \u201cH\u1eafn ta n\u00f3i r\u1eb1ng c\u1ea3 hai \u0111\u1ec1u \u0111\u00e3 ph\u1ea1m ph\u1ea3i sai l\u1ea7m v\u00e0 t\u00f4i kh\u00f4ng th\u00edch \u0111i\u1ec1u \u0111\u00f3 m\u1ed9t ch\u00fat n\u00e0o.\u201d<o:p></o:p></p>\r\n<p class=\"MsoNormal\" style=\"text-align:justify\">\u201cH\u1eafn ta v\u1eabn c\u00f2n h\u1ee3p \u0111\u1ed3ng \u1edf \u0111\u00e2y, nh\u01b0ng r\u1ed3i l\u1ea1i c\u00f3 c\u00e1ch h\u00e0nh x\u1eed kh\u00f4ng th\u1ec3 ch\u1ea5p nh\u1eadn \u0111\u01b0\u1ee3c, x\u1ee9ng \u0111\u00e1ng \u0111\u1ec3 t\u00f4i ch\u1ec9 tr\u00edch nh\u01b0ng r\u1ed3i v\u1eabn quy\u1ebft \u0111\u1ecbnh gi\u1eef im l\u1eb7ng. Gi\u1edd h\u1eafn ta \u0111\u00e3 \u0111i nh\u01b0ng c\u1ee9 ti\u1ebfp t\u1ee5c quay l\u1ea1i \u0111\u1ec3 b\u00f2n r\u00fat ch\u00fang t\u00f4i m\u1ed9t c\u00e1ch tham lam nh\u01b0 v\u1eady.\u201d<o:p></o:p></p>\r\n<p class=\"MsoNormal\" style=\"text-align:justify\">\u201cH\u1eafn \u0111ang mu\u1ed1n c\u01b0\u1edbp c\u1ea3 Napoli \u0111\u1ec3 mang \u0111\u1ebfn n\u01b0\u1edbc Anh, \u0111\u1ebfn n\u1ed7i t\u00f4i ph\u1ea3i ng\u1ed3i l\u1ea1i v\u1edbi c\u1ea3 BL\u0110 Chelsea \u0111\u1ec3 c\u00f3 th\u1ecfa thu\u1eadn. H\u1eafn mu\u1ed1n Jorginho th\u00ec ch\u00fang t\u00f4i \u0111\u00e3 cho to\u1ea1i nguy\u1ec7n, th\u1eadm ch\u00ed \u0111\u00e3 ph\u1ea3i thuy\u1ebft ph\u1ee5c t\u00e2n HLV Carlo Ancelotti n\u00ean \u0111\u1eb7t ni\u1ec1m tin nhi\u1ec1u h\u01a1n v\u00e0o Amadou Diawara ho\u1eb7c ch\u1ea5p nh\u1eadn k\u00e9o Marek Hamsik xu\u1ed1ng \u0111\u00e1 th\u1ea5p h\u01a1n.\u201d<o:p></o:p></p>\r\n<div style=\"text-align: justify;\">\r\n<div class=\"articlerelatepannel\">\r\n<div class=\"articlerelate2\"><span href=\"/bong-da-anh/huyen-thoai-chelsea-chinh-thuc-tro-ve-pho-ta-sarri-172-191564.html\"><img src=\"https://static.bongda24h.vn/medias/thumnail/2018/7/19/world-cup.jpg\" alt=\"\"></span><span href=\"/bong-da-anh/huyen-thoai-chelsea-chinh-thuc-tro-ve-pho-ta-sarri-172-191564.html\">Huy\u1ec1n tho\u1ea1i Chelsea ch\u00ednh th\u1ee9c tr\u1edf v\u1ec1 ph\u00f2 t\u00e1 Sarri</span><br>\r\nGianfranco Zola \u0111\u01b0\u1ee3c b\u1ed5 nhi\u1ec7m l\u00e0m tr\u1ee3 l\u00fd v\u00e0 s\u1ebd l\u00e0 c\u00e1nh tay ph\u1ea3i \u0111\u1eafc l\u1ef1c cho HLV \u0111\u1ed3ng h\u01b0\u01a1ng Maurizio Sarri trong ban hu\u1ea5n luy\u1ec7n Chelsea m\u00f9a gi\u1ea3i t\u1edbi \u0111\u00e2y.</div>\r\n</div>\r\n<strong>Gia Khoa (TTVN)</strong></div></div><advbottom>","new_url":"","id":"4478","checkdouble":"191768"}]}